%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Hosts%20Muslim%20World%20League%20Chief%20Al%20Issa%3A%20Outreach%20or%20Image%20Building%20PR%20Exercise%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24163521%2Fal-Issa-at-Akshardham.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20visit%20by%20the%20secretary%20general%20of%20the%20Muslim%20World%20League%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%E2%80%99s%20former%20minister%20for%20justice%2C%20Mohammad%20bin%20Abdulkarim%20Al-Issa%2C%20has%20reopened%20a%20debate%20on%20whether%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20revamp%20the%20image%20of%20its%20administration%20from%20one%20that%20is%20being%20increasingly%20identified%20with%20the%20persecution%20of%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAl-Issa%2C%20who%20is%20viewed%20as%20an%20advocate%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmoderate%20Islam%E2%80%9D%2C%20arrived%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20on%20July%2010%20for%20a%20five-day%20visit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20visit%20focused%20on%20interfaith%20relations%2C%20Islamic%20values%2C%20the%20need%20for%20communal%20harmony%2C%20and%20focusing%20on%20common%20interests%20which%20included%20separating%20Islam%20from%20the%20narrative%20of%20extremism%20and%20hatred.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20met%20top%20officials%20including%20President%20Draupadi%20Murmu%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20minority%20affairs%20minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20and%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%2C%20and%20called%20upon%20leading%20religious%20leaders%20and%20Muslim%20scholars.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20cultural-religious%20visit%20focused%20on%20deepening%20cooperation%20between%20the%20Muslim%20World%20League%20and%20India%20and%20its%20Muslims%2C%20critics%20say%20that%20the%20visit%20was%20more%20of%20a%20political%20exercise%20meant%20to%20benefit%20both%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EPleased%20with%20the%20extensive%20and%20fruitful%20meetings%20with%20the%20erudite%20scholars%20of%20India%2C%20and%20their%20brothers%20in%20citizenship%3B%20the%20Hindu%20religious%20leaders.%3Cbr%3E%5CnMany%20of%20the%20meetings%20brought%20together%20the%20diverse%20segments%20of%20Indian%20society%2C%20in%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20love%20and%20understanding.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FXh6Peiueql%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FXh6Peiueql%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Mohammed%20Al-Issa%20%D9%85%D8%AD%D9%85%D8%AF%20%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B9%D9%8A%D8%B3%D9%89%20(%40MhmdAlissa)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMhmdAlissa%2Fstatus%2F1681743646092132352%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2019%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAl-Issa%20described%20his%20meeting%20with%20Modi%20on%20July%2011%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinsightful%20discussion%E2%80%9D%20on%20a%20variety%20of%20issues.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20included%20ways%20to%20further%20human-centric%20development%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20promoting%20understanding%20and%20harmony%20among%20the%20followers%20of%20faith%20and%20culture.%20I%20appreciate%20His%20Excellency%E2%80%99s%20passionate%20perspective%20towards%20inclusive%20growth%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMhmdAlissa%2Fstatus%2F1679040162200780800%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewrote%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20Twitter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20also%20agreement%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20working%20together%20on%20confronting%20all%20aspects%20of%20extremism%20and%20hatred%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20source%20and%20reason%2C%20as%20peace%20and%20prosperity%20in%20our%20diverse%20world%20can%20only%20be%20achieved%20with%20aware%20and%20comprehensive%20citizenship.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20meeting%20Modi%2C%20Al-Issa%20delivered%20a%20lecture%20with%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval%20at%20the%20India%20Islamic%20Centre%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20where%20top%20Muslim%20leaders%20and%20scholars%20were%20invited.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20need%20of%20the%20hour%20(is)%20to%20establish%20communications%20between%20cultures.%20Diversity%20promotes%20good%20relationships%20between%20cultures.%20Unity%20in%20diversity%20is%20the%20way%20forward.%20Tolerance%20needs%20to%20become%20a%20part%20of%20our%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20Al-Issa%20said%20in%20his%20lecture%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20has%20been%20accessed%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAl-Issa%20said%20that%20the%20Muslim%20World%20League%20has%20alliances%20with%20different%20cultures%20of%20the%20world%20and%20praised%20India%E2%80%99s%20secular%20constitution%20despite%20being%20a%20Hindu%20majority%20nation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20many%20friends%20in%20the%20Hindu%20community.%20We%20wish%20to%20strengthen%20understanding%20between%20faiths.%20India%2C%20despite%20being%20a%20Hindu%20majority%20nation%2C%20has%20a%20secular%20constitution.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20deeply%20respect%20Sadhguru%20and%20Sri%20Sri%20Ravi%20Shankar.%20We%20have%20many%20common%20values%20with%20many%20Hindu%20leaders%20and%20we%20respect%20differences.%20We%20know%20the%20Muslim%20component%20is%20an%20important%20component.%20Indian%20Muslims%20are%20proud%20of%20being%20Indians.%20Religion%20can%20become%20a%20role%20for%20cooperation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20Al-Issa%20and%20Doval%20highlighted%20the%20importance%20of%20unity%20in%20diversity%20and%20the%20patriotic%20character%20of%20Indian%20Muslims.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20continues%20to%20play%20its%20role%20as%20a%20refuge%20for%20heterodox%20ideas%20with%20infinite%20capacity%20to%20absorb%20dissent.%20No%20religion%20is%20under%20threat%2C%E2%80%9D%20Doval%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faninews.in%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fno-religion-is-under-threat-in-india-nsa-ajit-doval20230711173833%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Equoted%20as%20saying%20by%20ANI.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20an%20inspiration%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20for%20being%20open%20to%20dialogue.%20Our%20partnership%20with%20India%20is%20a%20message%20to%20the%20whole%20world.%20This%20alliance%20of%20civilisations%20is%20a%20message%20of%20harmony%20to%20the%20whole%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20Al-Issa%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%2C%20Al-Issa%20also%20visited%20the%20Akshardham%20Temple%20in%20the%20capital%20and%20delivered%20a%20%3Ci%3Ekhutbah%3C%2Fi%3E%20(sermon)%20at%20the%20Jama%20Masjid%20%E2%80%93%20the%20first%20by%20a%20religious%20leader%20from%20outside%20the%20country%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.arabnews.com%2Fnode%2F2339596%2Fworld%5C%22%3Ein%20400%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20he%20once%20again%20reiterated%20that%20Islam%20stands%20against%20all%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrue-muslim-rejects-all-forms-of-extremism-muslim-world-leagues-al-issa-at-jama-masjid-101689407471408.html%5C%22%3Eforms%20of%20extremism%20and%20violence.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24162744%2FAl-Issa-at-Jama-Masjid-1024x683.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22705%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24162744%2FAl-Issa-at-Jama-Masjid-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24162744%2FAl-Issa-at-Jama-Masjid-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24162744%2FAl-Issa-at-Jama-Masjid.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664785%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22470%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAl-Issa%20visiting%20the%20Jama%20Masjid%20in%20Old%20Delhi.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40MhmdAlissa%2C%20July%2020%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%9CPositive%20message%20to%20Indian%20Muslims%20and%20the%20world%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReligious%20leaders%20who%20attended%20the%20event%20at%20the%20India%20Islamic%20Centre%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ethat%20Al-Issa%E2%80%99s%20visit%20and%20messaging%20were%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpositive%E2%80%9D%20initiative%20not%20just%20for%20Indian%20Muslims%20but%20for%20the%20international%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESyed%20Naseruddin%20Chishty%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Sufi%20Sajjadanashin%20Council%20and%20successor%20to%20the%20spiritual%20head%20of%20the%20Ajmer%20Dargah%20said%20that%20Al-Issa%E2%80%99s%20visit%20has%20sent%20out%20a%20message%20to%20the%20international%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20visit%20has%20been%20a%20very%20positive%20development.%20That%20a%20leader%20of%20such%20an%20important%2C%20reputed%20organisation%20has%20visited%20India%20is%20not%20just%20a%20message%20for%20Indians%20but%20also%20to%20the%20international%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEspecially%20in%20light%20of%20the%20fake%20propaganda%20that%20is%20being%20spread%20by%20some%20people%20about%20discrimination%20against%20Indian%20Muslims%20and%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20that%20Muslims%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20practice%20their%20own%20religion%20and%20Indian%20Muslims%20are%20facing%20persecution%20%E2%80%93%20Those%20who%20have%20been%20spreading%20this%20fake%20propaganda%20have%20been%20given%20a%20harsh%20answer.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20visit%20has%20proven%20that%20there%20is%20no%20discrimination%20and%20Muslims%20have%20all%20freedoms%20including%20political%20and%20religious.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2FAjit-Doval_PTI.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22National%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval.%20Credit%3A%20PTI%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-162000%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22182%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENational%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval.%20Credit%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAl-Issa%20said%20Islam%20only%20preaches%20love%20and%20peace%20and%20harmony.%20This%20message%20will%20resonate%20with%20the%20Indian%20Muslims.%20If%20we%20have%20to%20protect%20future%20generations%2C%20we%20have%20to%20go%20forward%20with%20both%20Al-Issa%20and%20Doval%E2%80%99s%20message%20of%20brotherhood%20and%20unity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHaji%20Syed%20Salman%20Chishty%2C%20chairman%2C%20Chishty%20Foundation%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGaddi-Nashin%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(Hereditary%20Custodians%2FKey%20Holders)%2C%20Dargah%20Ajmer%20Sharif%2C%20said%20that%20the%20historical%20and%20spiritual%20relations%20between%20India%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20have%20been%20enriched%20by%20the%20visit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20quite%20some%20time%20there%20were%20only%20bilateral%20relations.%20But%20with%20this%20visit%20by%20Sheikh%20Al-Issa%20%E2%80%93%20right%20from%20Jama%20Masjid%20to%20Akshardham%20Temple%20to%20all%20the%20other%20places%20that%20he%20went%20to%20%E2%80%93%20the%20message%20is%20very%20clear%20that%20we%20have%20to%20evolve%2C%20engage%20and%20rise%20above%20division%20and%20differences%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20message%20is%20not%20only%20between%20two%20countries%20but%20is%20a%20global%20message.%20Him%20reinstating%20the%20message%20of%20abiding%20by%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20reaffirms%20the%20message%20to%20work%20together%20to%20build%20the%20nation%20as%20our%20Constitution%20gives%20faith%20to%20all%20religions%20to%20amplify%20the%20noble%20message%20of%20all%20religions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20religious%20leaders%20said%20that%20the%20visit%2C%20though%20timed%20close%20to%20general%20elections%20next%20year%2C%20is%20only%20a%20coincidence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20elections%20are%20around%20the%20corner%20but%20it%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20Al-Issa.%20He%20is%20coming%20with%20a%20message%20that%20is%20unifying%20and%20is%20a%20global%20message%20and%20it%20is%20just%20a%20coincidence%20that%20elections%20are%20coming.%20There%20was%20no%20political%20messaging.%20The%20focus%20was%20on%20nation%20building%20and%20overcoming%20extremists%20and%20radicalisation%20and%20Islamic%20spiritual%20values%20of%20inclusiveness%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Salman%20Chishty.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%5BThere%20are%20only%5D%20isolated%20incidents%20of%20those%20who%20are%20indulging%20in%20hate%20speech.%20%3Cspan%3EIndia%20is%20a%20large%20country.%20We%20cannot%20say%20that%20this%20is%20happening%20everywhere%20and%20in%20every%20street%20and%20every%20corner.%20NSA%20Doval%E2%80%99s%20message%20was%20also%20very%20clear%20about%20unity%20in%20diversity.%20Incidents%20of%20hate%20speech%2C%20in%20the%20name%20of%20nationalism%20or%20in%20the%20name%20of%20targeting%20any%20religion%2C%20must%20be%20dealt%20with%20strictly%20within%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20constitution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felection-rhetoric-or-real-plan-opposition-raises-questions-as-bjp-broaches-ucc-yet-again%5C%22%3EElection%20Rhetoric%20or%20Real%20Plan%3F%20Opposition%20Raises%20Questions%20as%20BJP%20Broaches%20UCC%20Yet%20Again%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENaseruddin%20Chishty%20also%20said%20that%20those%20who%20are%20viewing%20this%20visit%20as%20an%20election%20strategy%20are%20showing%20their%20%E2%80%9Cnegative%E2%80%9D%20thoughts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20think%20that%20this%20has%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20elections%20have%20narrow%20and%20negative%20thoughts.%20If%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20done%20this%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20good%20thing.%20The%20message%20should%20go%20out%20that%20Indian%20Muslims%20love%20India%20and%20are%20proud%20of%20being%20Indians%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EEvolving%20domestic%20and%20foreign%20policies%20at%20play%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EObservers%20said%20that%20the%20visit%20needs%20to%20be%20examined%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20evolving%20domestic%20and%20foreign%20policies%20of%20both%20India%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20scholar%20who%20has%20worked%20closely%20on%20the%20region%20said%20that%20in%20the%20last%20sixty-odd%20years%2C%20the%20Muslim%20World%20League%20(MWL)%20has%20been%20the%20principal%20organisation%20for%20the%20promotion%20of%20the%20Saudi%20brand%20of%20Islam%2C%20referred%20to%20as%20Wahhabism%20%E2%80%93%20a%20rigid%2C%20narrow%20and%20doctrinaire%20expression%20of%20Islam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%2085vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24161240%2FMBS-1-300x200.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24161240%2FMBS-1-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24161240%2FMBS-1-1024x682.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24161240%2FMBS-1.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664777%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESaudi%20crown%20prince%20Mohammad%20bin%20Salman.%20Photo%3A%20Flickr%2FU.S.%20Department%20of%20State.%20Public%20domain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20has%20undergone%20a%20change%20in%20the%20last%20four-five%20years%20when%20the%20Saudi%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammad%20Bin%20Salman%20has%20been%20projecting%20his%20country%20as%20a%20modern%20and%20moderate%20kingdom%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20earlier%20rigid%20approach%20and%20the%20present%20moderate%20approach%20are%20both%20aimed%20at%20asserting%20the%20political%20interests%20of%20the%20kingdom%3A%20when%20earlier%2C%20with%20its%20affiliation%20with%20Wahhabism%2C%20the%20kingdom%20was%20asserting%20its%20leadership%20of%20the%20Muslim%20world.%20Now%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20is%20anxious%20to%20project%20itself%20as%20a%20modern%20nation%20that%20would%20be%20an%20attractive%20business%20partner%20for%20foreign%20companies%20and%20an%20attractive%20tourist%20destination.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20political%20gambit%20and%20has%20very%20little%20to%20do%20with%20faith.%20This%20was%20a%20PR%20effort%20made%20by%20the%20crown%20prince%20to%20project%20a%20new%20image%20of%20Islam%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20to%20different%20countries%20and%20enhance%20the%20image%20of%20the%20crown%20prince%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20his%20modern%20and%20dynamic%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20expert%20who%20has%20spent%20nearly%20two%20decades%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20has%20closely%20followed%20the%20politics%20of%20the%20Muslim%20world%20who%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20be%20named%20said%20that%20the%20role%20of%20the%20MWL%20is%20similar%20to%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COne%20can%20understand%20it%20the%20same%20way%20as%20the%20RSS%20in%20India%2C%20which%20sets%20its%20agenda%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion%20and%20presents%20PM%20Modi%20as%20Hindu%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHriday%20Samrat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSimilarly%2C%20the%20agenda%20of%20the%20MWL%20is%20run%20in%20the%20name%20of%20%E2%80%98Liberal%20Islam%E2%80%99.%20Although%20they%20have%20taken%20many%20reformist%20steps%20recently%2C%20especially%20in%20favour%20of%20women%2C%20there%20are%20many%20human%20rights%20issues%2C%20where%20one%20can%20hardly%20differentiate%20between%20the%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20narrow%20mindset%20and%20theirs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20far%20as%20the%20Indian%20Muslims%20are%20concerned%2C%20hardly%20any%20common%20Muslim%20expects%20anything%20from%20people%20like%20Al-Issa%20or%20from%20the%20Arab%20world.%20As%20holy%20as%20Saudi%20Arabia%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20by%20Muslims%2C%20the%20politics%20of%20the%20country%20is%20just%20as%20unholy%20as%20the%20politics%20in%20our%20own%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EConverging%20interests%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20former%20diplomat%20who%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20be%20named%2C%20the%20visit%20also%20reflects%20Saudi%E2%80%99s%20interests%20in%20India%2C%20which%20is%20a%20major%20buyer%20of%20crude%20oil%20from%20the%20kingdom.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20addition%2C%20the%20largest%20Indian%20community%20of%20Indian%20passport%20holders%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20is%20also%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia.%20India%20is%20also%20a%20major%20trade%20and%20investment%20partner.%20What%20we%20are%20seeing%20right%20now%20is%20the%20attempt%20to%20enhance%20and%20consolidate%20relations%20with%20India%20on%20bases%20that%20resonate%20well%20with%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20former%20diplomat%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20things%20which%20matters%20to%20the%20Modi%20government%20with%20regard%20to%20these%20engagements%20with%20these%20Muslim%20countries%20is%20to%20burnish%20its%20image%20at%20home%20about%20the%20mistreatment%20of%20minorities%2C%20particularly%20Muslims.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20engaging%20with%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20getting%20some%20of%20its%20people%20to%20praise%20India%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20able%20to%20pander%20to%20its%20own%20constituency.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Modi%20has%20faced%20criticism%20during%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhow-the-us-media-covered-modis-reception-by-biden-amidst-criticism-on-human-rights%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erecent%20trips%20to%20the%20US%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Ffrance-emmanuel-macron-narendra-modi-strategy%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EFrance%20for%20his%20handling%20of%20minority%20rights%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20country%2C%20such%20criticism%20has%20not%20shown%20any%20bearing%20on%20diplomatic%20relations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F22213452%2Fimage12.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F22213452%2Fimage12.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F22213452%2Fimage12-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-659669%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ETrucks%20carrying%20such%20banners%20urging%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20to%20question%20Modi%20were%20spotted%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20the%20New%20York%20City%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNeither%20are%20any%20of%20the%20western%20countries%20concerned%20about%20the%20state%20of%20democracy%20in%20India%20nor%20are%20any%20so-called%20%E2%80%9CMuslim%E2%80%9D%20countries%20concerned%20about%20the%20fate%20of%20Muslims%20in%20India.%20Political%20and%20economic%20interests%20trump%20all%20such%20considerations%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20former%20diplomat%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Modi%20government%20has%20no%20interest%20in%20foreign%20affairs%20and%20has%20no%20coherent%20foreign%20policy.%20It%20has%20only%20two%20guiding%20interests%20%E2%80%93%20to%20change%20the%20idea%20of%20India%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20Hindutva%20and%20make%20a%20Hindu%20Rashtra%2C%20a%20state%20which%20will%20be%20displaying%20characteristics%20of%20neo-Fascism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20second%20aspect%20is%20the%20persona%20of%20our%20leader%20%E2%80%93%20to%20project%20himself%20as%20a%20statesman%20and%20diplomat%2C%20and%20%5Bthat%5D%20in%20his%20individual%20personality%2C%20the%20salvation%20of%20the%20nation%20will%20be%20found.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20two%20ideas%20are%20not%20separate%2C%20they%20are%20integral%20to%20our%20national%20policy.%20Foreign%20affairs%E2%80%99%20entire%20purpose%20is%20to%20support%20the%20two-point%20agenda%20at%20home%2C%20as%20engaging%20abroad%20goes%20down%20very%20well%20with%20the%20constituency%20at%20home.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShaheen%20Nazar%2C%20former%20senior%20editor%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EArab%20News%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20said%20that%20the%20visit%20served%20a%20dual%20purpose.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20tour%20was%20about%20killing%20two%20birds%20with%20one%20stone.%20PM%20Modi%20has%20regularly%20visited%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20other%20Muslim%20countries.%20He%20has%20even%20been%20bestowed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Findia-news-india%2Fmodi-saudi-arabia-king-abdulaziz-sash-civilian-honour%2F%5C%22%3Ehighest%20civilian%20honour%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20too%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Muslims%20and%20Dalits%20were%2C%20and%20still%20are%2C%20being%20lynched%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20it%20is%20quite%20clear%20that%20Saudi%20Arabia%20cares%20little%20for%20such%20issues.%20However%2C%20PM%20Modi%20is%20keen%20on%20showing%20the%20western%20world%20and%20international%20media%20that%20the%20Muslim%20world%20is%20standing%20beside%20him%20despite%20their%20%E2%80%98propaganda%E2%80%99%20about%20the%20plight%20of%20Indian%20Muslims.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20in%20fact%20a%20special%20type%20of%20diplomacy%20which%20is%20directly%20benefiting%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20Ajit%20Doval%20is%20an%20expert%20in%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnarendra-modi-islamic-nations-egypt-eid-gujarat-lynching%5C%22%3EEgypt%E2%80%99s%20Paeans%20to%20Narendra%20Modi%20Cannot%20Erase%20the%20Past%20or%20Present%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENazar%20added%20that%20figures%20like%20Al-Issa%20cannot%20speak%20much%20about%20democracy%20and%20coexistence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20can%20people%20like%20Al-Issa%20say%20about%20%E2%80%98democracy%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98coexistence%E2%80%99%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20only%20repeated%20what%20he%20was%20told%20to%20say.%20He%20is%20close%20to%20the%20royal%20family%20and%20the%20organisations%20he%20is%20associated%20with%2C%20be%20it%20the%20Muslim%20World%20League%20or%20the%20Organization%20of%20Islamic%20Cooperation%2C%20all%20mask%20their%20foreign%20policy.%20Most%20Muslims%20do%20not%20even%20know%20about%20them.%20They%20rule%20over%20a%20conservative%20society%2C%20and%20are%20now%20trying%20to%20carve%20a%20liberal%20image%20for%20themselves%20in%20the%20name%20of%20reform.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20still%20maintain%20that%20they%20will%20not%2C%20and%20cannot%2C%20speak%20up%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20Indian%20Muslims.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20nothing%20to%20offer%20in%20advice%20either.%20But%20Modi%20had%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20visit%2C%20which%20he%20did.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHow%20common%20Muslims%20benefitted%20from%20the%20visit%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EObservers%20said%20that%20the%20people%20who%20met%20Al-Issa%20are%20hardly%20representative%20of%20the%20common%20Muslim%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAl-Issa%20is%20not%20a%20familiar%20figure%20among%20Muslims%2C%20but%20he%20was%20sent%20to%20Akshardham%20along%20with%20a%20handful%20of%20elite%20Muslims%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eof%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0their%20organisation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nazar%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20all%20close%20to%20the%20government%2C%20close%20to%20the%20BJP.%20They%20cannot%20take%20to%20the%20streets%20and%20raise%20the%20issues%20of%20Muslims.%20You%20must%20understand%20that%20none%20of%20the%20Muslims%20he%20met%20were%20truly%20a%20representative%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20They%20are%20wealthy%20Muslims.%20So%2C%20what%20was%20it%20about%3F%20Do%20you%20think%20they%20could%20have%20any%20interest%20in%20Indian%20Muslims%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20question%20is%20%E2%80%93%20what%20were%20our%20religious%20leaders%20doing%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSaudi%20Arabia%20is%20a%20necessity%20for%20them.%20They%20get%20them%20to%20stay%20in%20five%20star%20hotels.%20They%20have%20no%20say%20with%20the%20government%20of%20the%20country.%20They%20are%20paid%20stooges%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ewazifa%20khwars%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20Arabs.%20If%20you%20ask%20them%20about%20this%20visit%2C%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20utter%20a%20word.%20If%20they%20had%20the%20courage%2C%20they%20would%20have%20spoken%20up%20about%20the%20condition%20of%20Indian%20Muslims%20in%20front%20of%20him%20(Al-Issa).%20But%20they%20could%20not.%20Each%20of%20them%20has%20their%20own%20interests.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMir%20Ayoob%20Ali%20Khan%2C%20who%20worked%20as%20the%20Deputy%20Managing%20Editor%20in-charge%20of%20national%20and%20international%20Affairs%20at%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESaudi%20Gazette%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20is%20currently%20associated%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Siasat%20Daily%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20said%20that%20Al-Issa%20only%20met%20those%20people%20%E2%80%9Cwhom%20Ajit%20Doval%20chose%2C%20and%20he%20chose%20only%20those%20who%20speak%20well%20about%20Modi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20PR%20exercise%2C%20led%20by%20Doval%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EQuestioning%20why%20Al-Issa%20did%20not%20speak%20to%20any%20Muslim%20organisation%20in%20India%2C%20Khan%20asked%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20was%20the%20purpose%20of%20his%20visit%20then%3F%20These%20are%20the%20people%20who%20have%20been%20fighting%20against%20idols%20their%20entire%20life%20and%20are%20now%20visiting%20those%20very%20places.%20What%20message%20do%20they%20want%20to%20convey%20by%20doing%20so%3F%20That%20they%20have%20changed%20their%20stance%20or%20have%20we%20changed%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F24040310%2FModi-Crown-Prince-21.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F24040310%2FModi-Crown-Prince-21.jpg%20875w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F24040310%2FModi-Crown-Prince-21-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340121%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIndia%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20have%20generally%20warm%20relations.%20Credit%3A%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20ask%20me%20why%20this%20is%20happening%2C%20I%20do%20not%20have%20a%20clear%20picture%20of%20his%20foreign%20policy.%20Secondly%2C%20we%20do%20not%20even%20know%20the%20opinion%20of%20Saudi%20Arabia%20about%20India.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20they%20are%20friends%20with%20Pakistan.%20Then%20they%20are%20joining%20hands%20with%20Turkey%20and%20Iran%20as%20well.%20And%20now%20they%20are%20striking%20a%20friendship%20with%20India%20in%20the%20same%20backdrop.%20How%20can%20they%20benefit%20from%20it%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Muslim%20leadership%20of%20India%20is%20completely%20divided%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20it%20is%20a%20very%20confusing%20situation%20about%20Muslims%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Shakeel%20Rasheed%2C%20editor%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMumbai%20Urdu%20News%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20there%20was%20no%20need%20for%20Al-Issa%20to%20remark%20on%20the%20nationalism%20of%20Indian%20Muslims.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBecause%20Indian%20Muslims%20are%20undoubtedly%20proud%20of%20their%20Indianness%20and%20their%20constitution%2C%20and%20they%20also%20consider%20co-existence%20necessary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20at%20all%20he%20had%20to%20say%20something%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20better%20to%20point%20out%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Ajit%20Doval%20how%20coexistence%20calls%20for%20the%20majority%20to%20take%20along%20the%20minorities%20of%20the%20country%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Dalits%2C%20backwards%2C%20tribals%20and%20the%20economically%20weaker%20sections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERasheed%20added%20that%20on%20his%20part%2C%20while%20Al-Issa%20could%20not%20and%20should%20not%20interfere%20with%20the%20internal%20affairs%20of%20an%20independent%20country%2C%20as%20a%20guest%20and%20friend%20of%20this%20country%2C%20he%20could%20at%20least%20have%20given%20a%20message%20of%20peace%20and%20through%20this%20message%20he%20could%20have%20conveyed%20the%20true%20meaning%20of%20co-existence%20to%20the%20authorities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20it%20is%20enough%20that%20instead%20of%20calling%20Indian%20Muslims%20terrorists%2C%20he%20called%20them%20nationalist.%20It%20is%20not%20as%20if%20they%20do%20not%20know%20the%20situation%2C%20but%20they%20have%20their%20own%20vested%20interests.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690201200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24163521%2Fal-Issa-at-Akshardham.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-hosts-mwl-chief-outreach-or-pr%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mohammad%20bin%20Abdulkarim%20Al-Issa's%20five-day%20visit%20focused%20on%20interfaith%20relations%2C%20Islamic%20values%2C%20the%20need%20for%20communal%20harmony%2C%20and%20on%20common%20interests.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Conservatives%20Win%20Election%20In%20Spain%2C%20But%20Battle%20For%20Parliamentary%20Majority%20Still%20On%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24173615%2FPP-Feijoo-X.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ESpain%E2%80%99s%20opposition%C2%A0right-wing%20Popular%20Party%20(PP)%20won%20Sunday%E2%80%99s%20snap%20general%20election%2C%20with%C2%A0100%25%20of%20the%20votes%20counted%2C%20but%20was%20set%20to%20fall%20short%20of%20a%20parliamentary%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PP%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Pedro%20Sanchez%E2%80%99%20Socialist%20Workers%E2%80%99%20Party%C2%A0(PSOE)%20had%C2%A033.1%25%C2%A0and%2031.7%25%20shares%20of%20the%20vote%C2%A0respectively%2C%20the%C2%A0results%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20would%20give%20the%20PP%2C%20under%20leader%20Alberto%20Nunez%20Feijoo%2C%20136%C2%A0seats%20in%20the%20350-seat%C2%A0lower%20chamber%2C%20the%20Congress%20of%20Deputies%2C%20and%20the%20Socialists%C2%A0122%C2%A0seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EParties%20now%20look%20to%20form%20coalition%20government%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PP%20now%C2%A0requires%20support%20from%20several%20junior%20parties%C2%A0to%20achieve%C2%A0a%20governing%20majority%20of%20176%20seats%2C%20so%C2%A0the%20result%20is%20likely%20to%20produce%20weeks%20of%20political%20jockeying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20far-right%20Vox%2C%20which%20offered%20to%20partner%20with%20the%20PP%2C%20was%20projected%20to%20win%2033%20seats.%20But%20even%20with%20the%20169%20seats%20this%20would%20amount%20to%2C%20the%20PP%20would%20still%20be%20seven%20seats%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20that%20partnership%20is%20later%20confirmed%2C%20along%20with%20a%20third%20party%2C%20it%20would%20be%20the%20first%20time%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ffar-right-populism-in-europe%2Ft-66108914%5C%22%3Efar-right%20party%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20entered%20government%20in%20Spain%20since%20Francisco%20Franco%E2%80%99s%20dictatorship%20ended%20in%20the%201970s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20radical%20left-wing%20Sumar%2C%20which%20brought%20together%2015%20small%20leftist%20parties%20and%C2%A0backed%20the%20Socialists%2C%20won%C2%A031%C2%A0seats%2C%20giving%20their%20alliance%20just%20153%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remaining%20parties%20are%20mostly%20region-specific.%20The%20two%20Catalan%20pro-independence%20parties%2C%20who%20voted%20to%20support%20a%20Sanchez-lead%20government%20previously%2C%C2%A0saw%20their%20number%20of%20seats%20fall%2C%20but%20may%20still%20play%20the%20role%20of%20kingmaker%20if%20Sanchez%20tries%20to%20stay%20on%20as%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPossible%20demands%20from%20the%20separatist%20Catalan%20party%20Junts%20(Together)%20for%20a%20referendum%20on%20Catalonia%E2%80%99s%20independence%20could%20be%20an%20obstacle%20to%20Sanchez%20bringing%20it%20on%20board%20in%20a%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20failure%20by%20both%20sides%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20governing%20coalition%20could%20result%20in%20yet%20another%20election%20being%20called.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESanchez%20and%20Feijoo%20both%20claim%20victory%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PP%20leader%C2%A0told%20supporters%20in%20Madrid%20on%20Sunday%20evening%20that%20his%20party%20would%20now%20try%20to%20form%20a%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20candidate%20of%20the%20party%20that%20won%20the%20most%20seats%2C%20I%20believe%20it%20is%20my%20duty%20to%20try%20to%20form%20a%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20Feijoo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asked%20that%20%E2%80%9Cno%20one%20fall%20into%20the%20temptation%20of%20blocking%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20new%20government%E2%80%9D%2C%20adding%20that%20Spain%20did%20not%20need%20a%20period%20of%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchez%20was%20also%20celebrating%20the%20result%C2%A0from%20the%20balcony%20of%20his%20party%20headquarters%20late%20Sunday%2C%20as%20the%20Socialists%20had%20won%C2%A0more%20seats%20and%20a%20higher%20percentage%20of%20the%20votes%20than%20in%20the%202019%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20supporters%20that%20the%20projected%20win%20of%20the%20conservative%20and%20far-right%20block%20had%20failed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20backward-looking%20bloc%2C%20which%20proposed%20a%20total%20repeal%20of%20all%20the%20progress%20we%20have%20made%20over%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20has%20failed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20regressive%20block%20made%20up%20of%20the%20Popular%20Party%20and%20Vox%20were%20beaten.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20more%20who%20want%20Spain%20to%20keep%20advancing%20than%20those%20who%20want%20to%20step%20backward%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sanchez%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20did%20S