our%20rooms%20in%20this%20process.%20Now%20it%20is%20difficult%20for%20my%20family%20to%20adjust%20in%20this%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tripathi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESP%20trade%20unionist%20Nandu%20Gupta%20fears%20that%20in%20order%20to%20enhance%20the%20aesthetics%20of%20the%20newly%20constructed%20road%20leading%20to%20the%20temple%2C%20the%20administration%20will%20also%20clear%20the%20street%20vendors%20and%20small%20%3Cem%3Ethela%3C%2Fem%3E%20owners%20who%20have%20been%20earning%20their%20livelihoods%20on%20the%20roadside.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGupta%20said%20that%20he%20and%20his%20comrades%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20deity%20Ram%2C%20asking%20him%20to%20protect%20his%20Ayodhya%20and%20its%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690198219000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24162930%2FIMG_2541.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Furban%2Fayodhya-rampath-demolition-construction%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amidst%20rampant%20construction%20and%20demolition%20efforts%2C%20at%20risk%20are%20people%E2%80%99s%20houses%2C%20businesses%20and%20a%20275-year-old%20mosque.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Furban%2Fayodhya-rampath-demolition-construction%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20agrees%20to%20examine%20EC's%20delimitation%20powers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690198050000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102080938%2Cimgsize-31530.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsc-agrees-to-examine-constitutional-validity-of-election-commission-undertaking-delimitation-of-constituencies%2Farticleshow%2F102080929.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%20agreed%20to%20examine%20the%20constitutional%20vali