zen%20states%2C%20including%20Karnataka%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Bihar%20and%20Haryana%2C%20saw%20a%20decline%20between%202021-22%20and%202022-23%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20(WCD)%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20occurred%20despite%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1695199%5C%22%3Esuccess%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Beti%20Bachao%20Beti%20Padhao%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20scheme%20by%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%2C%20which%20uses%20sex%20ratio%20at%20birth%20as%20a%20parameter%20for%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fnational%2Fover-dozen-states-saw-decline-in-sex-ratio-since-2020-govt-1240024.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ladakh%20stands%20out%20as%20the%20only%20state%2FUnion%20territory%20in%20the%20country%20where%20the%20number%20of%20girl%20children%20is%20more%20than%20boys.%20It%20has%20a%20sex%20ratio%20of%201%2C023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20states%20like%20Rajasthan%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Assam%2C%20Kerala%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20sex%20ratio%20has%20shown%20an%20improvement%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20sex%20ratio%20fell%20from%20949%20in%202020%E2%80%9321%20to%20940%20in%202021%E2%80%9322%2C%20but%20there%20was%20a%20slight%20recovery%20in%202022%E2%80%9323%20when%20it%20marginally%20rose%20to%20945.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Delhi%2C%20the%20sex%20ratio%20was%20927%20in%202020%E2%80%9321%2C%20fell%20to%20924%20in%202021%E2%80%9322%2C%20and%20further%20fell%20to%20916%20in%202022%E2%80%9323.%20The%20sex%20ratio%20in%20West%20Bengal%20fell%20from%20949%20in%202020%E2%80%9321%20to%20943%20in%202021%E2%80%9322%20and%20then%20to%20932%20in%202022%E2%80%9323%2C%20said%20the%20government%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%20saw%20a%20decline%20from%20917%20in%202020%E2%80%9321%20to%20915%20in%202021%E2%80%9322%2C%20and%20then%20fell%20to%20895%20in%202022%E2%80%9323.%20Chandigarh%2C%20too%2C%20registered%20a%20steep%20fall.%20It%20first%20rose%20from%20935%20in%202020%E2%80%9321%20to%20941%20in%202021%E2%80%9322%2C%20and%20then%20down%20to%20902%20in%202022%E2%80%9323.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Himachal%2C%20it%20fell%20from%20944%20in%202020%E2%80%9321%20to%20941%20in%202021%E2%80%9322%20and%20932%20in%202022%E2%80%9323.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20states%20like%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Assam%20and%20Kerala%2C%20the%20sex%20ratio%20showed%20improvement.%20In%20UP%2C%20it%20first%20fell%20from%20940%20in%202020-21%20to%20939%20in%202021-22%20but%20then%20improved%20to%20944%20in%202022-23.%20In%20Assam%2C%20it%20rose%20from%20942%20in%202020-21%20to%20944%20in%202021-22%2C%20and%20then%20further%20rose%20to%20951%20in%202022-23.%20In%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20sex%20ratio%20(946)%20remained%20the%20same%20in%20all%20three%20years%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20daily%20further%20said%20that%20several%20states%20had%20significant%20amounts%20of%20unutilised%20funds%20that%20were%20allocated%20for%20the%20scheme%20by%20the%20WCD%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20in%202020%E2%80%9321%2C%20Haryana%20utilised%20only%20Rs%20142.26%20lakh%20of%20the%20Rs%20249.83%20lakh%2C%20and%20in%202021%E2%80%9322%2C%20it%20used%20only%20Rs%2027.09%20lakh%20of%20the%20Rs%20162.8%20lakh%20it%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20utilised%20Rs%20742.60%20lakh%20in%202020%E2%80%9321%20even%20when%20Rs%20577.95%20lakh%20was%20released%20under%20the%20scheme%2C%20but%20in%202021%E2%80%9322%2C%20it%20used%20only%20Rs%20162.89%20lakh%20of%20the%20Rs%201%2C499.45%20lakh%20that%20was%20allocated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20raises%20questions%20about%20the%20effective%20implementation%20and%20management%20of%20the%20allocated%20resources%20under%20the%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690197620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F10%2Fhandpump.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsex-ratio-falls-in-several-states-despite-niti-aayog-success-report-on-beti-bachao-beti-padhao%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ladakh%20stands%20out%20as%20the%20only%20state%2FUnion%20territory%20in%20the%20country%20where%20the%20number%20of%20girl%20children%20is%20more%20than%20boys%2C%20with%20a%20sex%20ratio%20of%201%2C023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsex-ratio-falls-in-several-states-despite-niti-aayog-success-report-on-beti-bachao-beti-padhao%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%202%20digital%20rights%20sold%20for%20200%20crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690197537000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102080496%2Cimgsize-18794.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Findian-2-digital-rights-of-kamal-haasans-film-sold-for-rs-200-crore-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F102080567.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102080567.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBuzz%20ofr%20Kamal%20Hassan's%20Indian%202%20is%20so%20high%20that%20a%20streaming%20giant%20has%20paid%20nealry%20200%20crores%20for%20its%20rights%20across%20langauges.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Jigar%20Shah%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Findian-2-digital-rights-of-kamal-haasans-film-sold-for-rs-200-crore-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F102080567.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22