w%2C%20that%20includes%20a%20wide%20definition%20of%20beef%2C%20if%20violated%2C%20would%20lead%20to%20a%20punishment%20of%20up%20to%20ten%20years%20with%20fine%20ranging%20between%20Rs%2030%2C000%20to%20a%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20has%20recorded%20very%20low%20conviction%20rates%20with%20vigilantism%20continuing%20in%20Haryana%20despite%20its%20introduction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Bharadwaj%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20restaurants%20are%20polluting%20Gurugram%E2%80%99s%20environment%20and%20hurting%20Hindu%20sentiments.%20If%20the%20restaurant%20claims%20that%20what%20they%20were%20selling%20was%20not%20beef%20but%20buffalo%2C%20then%20they%20should%20lodge%20a%20complaint%20against%20the%20food%20vlogger%20who%20was%20broadcasting%20otherwise%20on%20his%20Instagram%20page.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20visiting%20restaurant%20Haru%20in%20South%20Point%20Mall%2C%20Gurugram%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20told%20by%20its%20staff%20that%20a%20police%20delegation%20visited%20the%20restaurant%20to%20collect%20the%20samples%20of%20the%20meet.%20The%20chef%20of%20the%20restaurant%2C%20Kamal%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20selling%20buffalo%20tongue%2C%20but%20buff%20is%20known%20as%20beef%20in%20the%20Korean%20community.%E2%80%9D%20They%20also%20informed%20us%20that%20they%20are%20unwilling%20to%20publicise%20the%20matter%20until%20the%20report%20results%20are%20released%20and%20will%20probably%20consider%20action%20against%20the%20individual%20vlogger%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssistant%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%2C%20Varun%20Dahiya%20said%20the%20result%20of%20the%20report%20is%20expected%20in%20the%20next%20month%20and%20a%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FLTDmn9UGR5k%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20