%20part%20of%20the%20money%20was%20converted%20into%20cryptocurrency%20and%20deposited%20into%20a%20wallet%20operated%20by%20Hezbollah.%20Nine%20people%20have%20been%20arrested%20-%20four%20from%20Hyderabad%2C%20three%20from%20Mumbai%20and%20two%20from%20Ahmedabad%20-%20and%20the%20police%20are%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20at%20least%20six%20more.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cyber%20crime%20branch%20of%20the%20Hyderabad%20police%2C%20which%20began%20investigating%20the%20case%20in%20April%20after%20being%20approached%20by%20a%20person%20who%20said%20he%20had%20been%20conned%20of%20Rs%2028%20lakh%2C%20found%20that%20people%20were%20lured%20in%20the%20name%20of%20investment-cum-part-time-jobs.%20They%20were%20asked%20to%20do%20simple%20tasks%2C%20such%20as%20liking%20YouTube%20videos%20or%20writing%20Google%20reviews%2C%20and%20were%20paid%20for%20completing%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victims%2C%20who%20have%20lost%20Rs%205-6%20lakh%20on%20average%2C%20were%20approached%20on%20Telegram%20and%20Whatsapp.%20They%20invested%20small%20amounts%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%205%2C000%20and%20were%20given%20high%20returns%2C%20including%20double%20the%20money%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20after%20completing%20the%20first%20task.%20The%20investors%20were%20then%20asked%20to%20put%20in%20higher%20amounts%20in%20a%20series%20of%207-8%20transactions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fake%20window%20showed%20the%20money%20purportedly%20earned%20by%20the%20investors%2C%20but%20they%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20withdraw%20the%20money%20till%20they%20completed%20all%20the%20tasks.%20By%20then%2C%20they%20had%20already%20put%20in%20several%20lakhs%20of%20rupees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20one%20Shiva%20approached%20the%20Hyderabad%20cyber%20crime%20branch%20in%20April%2C%20saying%20he%20had%20been%20duped%20of%20Rs%2028%20lakh%20by%20cyber%20fraudsters%2C%20investigators%20found%2048%20bank%20accounts%2C%20which%20had%20been%20set%20up%20in%20the%20name%20of%20shell%20companies.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20agency%20believed%20that%20the%20fraud%20was%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%20584%20crores.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20another%20Rs%20128%20crore%20had%20been%20swindled%20by%20the%20scamsters.%20A%20total%20of%20113%20Indian%20bank%20accounts%20were%20used%20in%20the%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20moved%20through%20multiple%20accounts%20and%20was%20converted%20into%20cryptocurrency.%20It%20was%20then%20routed%20to%20China%20through%20Dubai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20accounts%2C%20which%20were%20opened%20in%20India%20using%20Indian%20SIM%20cards%2C%20were%20subsequently%20remotely%20operated%20in%20Dubai.%20The%20fraudsters%20were%20in%20touch%20with%20Chinese%20operators%2C%20who%20are%20the%20masterminds%20of%20the%20scam%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20police%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20account%20was%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Hyderabad-based%20Radhika%20Marketing%20Company%20and%20was%20linked%20to%20a%20phone%20number%20registered%20in%20the%20name%20of%20one%20Munawar%2C%20who%20is%20also%20from%20the%20city.%20Munawar%20had%20gone%20to%20Lucknow%20with%20three%20aides%20-%20Arul%20Das%2C%20Shah%20Sumair%20and%20Sameer%20Khan%20-%20and%20they%20opened%2065%20accounts%20of%2033%20shell%20companies.%20They%20were%20paid%20Rs%202%20lakh%20for%20each%20account%20and%20were%20arrested%20after%20the%20police%20traced%20Munawar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20their%20interrogation%2C%20they%20told%20the%20police%20that%20the%20accounts%20were%20opened%20on%20the%20direction%20of%20three%20other%20people%20involved%20in%20the%20scam%2C%20whom%20they%20have%20only%20identified%20as%20Manish%2C%20Vikas%20and%20Rajesh.%20The%20police%20are%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20these%20three%20men.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2065%20accounts%20were%20then%20used%20by%20the%20Chinese%20masterminds%20-%20Kevin%20Jun%2C%20Lee%20Lou%20Langzhou%20and%20Shasha%20-%20to%20move%20over%20Rs%20128%20crore.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn.%3Cbr%3E%5CnDetails%20of%20the%20transactions%20revealed%20that%20some%20of%20the%20accounts%20were%20being%20operated%20by%20a%20Dubai-based%20group%20using%20remote-access%20apps.%20The%20people%20in%20the%20Dubai%20group%20had%20connections%20with%20the%20Chinese%20network%20and%20were%20transferring%20money%20into%20crypto%20wallets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20wallets%20used%20for%20this%20were%20owned%20by%20Ahmedabad-based%20Prakash%20Mulchandbhai%20Prajapati%20and%20Kumar%20Prajapati%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20have%20now%20been%20arrested.%20A%20police%20officer%20said%20Prakash%20used%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20Chinese%20handlers%20and%20shared%20the%20bank%20account%20details%20and%20other%20information%20with%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20said%20three%20people%20have%20also%20been%20arrested%20from%20Mumbai%20and%20they%20have%20information%20about%20at%20least%20six%20people%20based%20in%20Dubai%20who%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20scam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690195920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-10%2Fcyber-crime-generic-650_650x400_71476249373.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F15-000-indians-conned-of-rs-700-crore-fraudsters-have-china-terror-links-4236308%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20police%20have%20unearthed%20a%20fraud%20ring%20involving%20Chinese%20handlers%20in%20which%2015%2C000%20Indians%20were%20duped%20of%20over%20Rs%20700%20crore.%20The%20money%20was%20routed%20to%20China%20and%20some%20of%20it%20was%20also%20sent%20to%20an%20account%20operated%20by%20the%20terror%20group%20Hezbollah.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F15-000-indians-conned-of-rs-700-crore-fraudsters-have-china-terror-links-4236308%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-