ur%20states%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20directed%20the%20states%20and%20Union%20Territories%20(UTs)%20that%20have%20failed%20to%20submit%20their%20responses%20to%20do%20so%20by%20August%2031%20positively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20states%20which%20are%20in%20default%20are%20placed%20on%20notice%20that%20should%20there%20be%20any%20further%20default%2C%20this%20court%20will%20be%20constrained%20to%20take%20recourse%20to%20the%20coercive%20arm%20of%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20bench%2C%20also%20comprising%20Justices%20JB%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Solicitor%20General%20Aishwarya%20Bhati%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Centre%2C%20told%20the%20bench%20the%20central%20government%20has%20received%20inputs%20from%20only%20four%20states%20-%20Haryana%2C%20Delhi%2C%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20-%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20had%20on%20April%2010%20asked%20the%20Centre%20to%20prepare%20a%20Standard%20Operating%20Procedure%20(SOPs)%20and%20formulate%20a%20national%20model%20to%20be%20adopted%20by%20all%20states%20and%20UTs%20to%20manage%20the%20menstrual%20hygiene%20of%20school-going%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20the%20issue%20is%20of%20%26quot%3Bimmense%20importance%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20top%20court%20said%20the%20Centre%20should%20engage%20with%20all%20stakeholders%20to%20implement%20a%20uniform%20national%20policy%20on%20managing%20menstrual%20hygiene%20in%20schools%2C%20including%20in%20government%20and%20government-aided%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20seized%20of%20a%20plea%20which%20has%20sought%20direction%20to%20the%20Centre%2C%20states%20and%20UTs%20to%20ensure%20the%20provision%20of%20free%20sanitary%20pads%20to%20every%20girl%20studying%20between%20classes%206%20and%2012%20and%20separate%20toilets%20for%20them%20in%20all%20government-aided%20and%20residential%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%20on%20Monday%2C%20Ms%20Bhati%20told%20the%20bench%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20earlier%20given%20extensive%20directions%20to%20frame%20or%20update%20a%20national%20policy%20on%20menstrual%20hygiene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20Lordships%20had%20directed%20the%20states%20to%20give%20their%20inputs%20to%20us%20within%20four%20weeks.%20Unfortunately%2C%20we%20got%20it%20only%20from%20four%20states%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20states%20and%20UTs%20may%20be%20given%20a%20last%20opportunity%20to%20share%20their%20inputs%20with%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20noted%20that%20Ms%20Bhati%20has%20stated%20that%20under%20the%20top%20court's%20April%2010%20order%2C%20responses%20have%20been%20received%20by%20the%20Centre%20only%20from%20Delhi%2C%20Haryana%2C%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20direct%20all%20other%20states%20and%20UTs%20which%20have%20failed%20to%20submit%20their%20responses%20to%20do%20so%20positively%20by%20August%2031%2C%202023%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20copy%20of%20its%20order%20should%20be%20made%20available%20to%20the%20chief%20secretaries%20of%20the%20remaining%20states%20for%20compliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20posted%20the%20matter%20for%20further%20hearing%20in%20the%20second%20week%20of%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%2010%2C%20the%20top%20court%20appointed%20the%20secretary%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%20(MOHFW)%20as%20the%20nodal%20officer%20to%20coordinate%20with%20the%20states%20and%20UTs%20and%20collect%20relevant%20data%20to%20formulate%20a%20national%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20noted%20that%20MoHFW%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20and%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Jal%20Shakti%20have%20schemes%20on%20menstrual%20hygiene%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20present%20stage%2C%20we%20are%20of%20the%20considered%20view%20that%20it%20would%20be%20appropriate%20if%20the%20Union%20government%20engages%20with%20all%20the%20state%20governments%20and%20Union%20Territories%20to%20ensure%20that%20a%20uniform%20national%20policy%20is%20formulated%20with%20sufficient%20leeway%20for%20the%20states%20and%20Union%20Territories%20to%20make%20adjustments%2C%20based%20on%20the%20prevailing%20conditions%20in%20their%20territories%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20top%20court%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20directed%20that%20all%20states%20and%20UTs%20must%20submit%20their%20menstrual%20hygiene%20management%20strategies%20and%20plans%20which%20are%20being%20executed%20either%20with%20the%20help%20of%20funds%20provided%20by%20the%20Centre%20or%20through%20their%20resources%20to%20the%20Mission%20Steering%20Group%20of%20the%20National%20Health%20Mission%20within%20four%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20said%20the%20states%20and%20UTs%20shall%20also%20indicate%20to%20the%20Mission%20Steering%20Group%20of%20the%20National%20Health%20Mission%20the%20appropriate%20ratio%20of%20female%20toilets%20for%20residential%20and%20non-residential%20schools%20in%20their%20respective%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20asked%20all%20states%20and%20UTs%20to%20also%20indicate%20the%20steps%20which%20have%20been%20taken%20to%20provide%20low-cost%20sanitary%20pads%20and%20vending%20machines%20in%20schools%20and%20their%20appropriate%20disposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20affidavit%20filed%20before%20the%20top%20court%2C%20the%20health%20ministry%20said%20it%20had%20undertaken%20awareness%20and%20training%20programmes%20and%20made%20necessary%20resources%20available%20to%20girls%20nationwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%20filed%20in%20the%20top%20court%20said%20that%20adolescent%20girls%20from%20poor%20backgrounds%20between%20the%20age%20of%2011%20and%2018%20face%20serious%20difficulties%20in%20receiving%20education%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20educati