k%20had%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20bank%20has%20also%20imposed%20penalties%20on%20several%20cooperative%20banks%20for%20contravention%20of%20its%20different%20norms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%20last%20year%2C%20it%20issued%20fresh%20instructions%20barring%20recovery%20agents%20from%20resorting%20to%20intimidation%20of%20borrowers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20calling%20them%20before%208%20am%20and%20after%207%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690194300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fls6cpet4_nirmala-sitharaman-ndtv_625x300_23_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbank-recovery-agents-loan-repayment-no-harsh-steps-finance-minister-nirmala-sitharaman-says-instructed-banks-on-merciless-loan-recovery-4236330%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20today%20said%20the%20government%20has%20instructed%20both%20public%20and%20private%20banks%20that%20harsh%20steps%20should%20not%20be%20taken%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20process%20of%20loan%20repayment%20and%20that%20they%20should%20handle%20such%20cases%20with%20humanity%20and%20sensitivity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbank-recovery-agents-loan-repayment-no-harsh-steps-finance-minister-nirmala-sitharaman-says-instructed-banks-on-merciless-loan-recovery-4236330%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbank-recovery-agents-loan-repayment-no-harsh-steps-finance-minister-nirmala-sitharaman-says-instructed-banks-on-merciless-loan-recovery-4236330%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbank-recovery-agents-loan-repayment-no-harsh-steps-finance-minister-nirmala-sitharaman-says-instructed-banks-on-merciless-loan-recovery-4236330%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Happiness%20for%20Beginners%E2%80%99%20Rev