%2C%20shiver%20and%20even%20sweat.%20ANDI%20has%20been%20developed%20by%20researchers%20at%20Arizona%20State%20University%20in%20the%20US.%20And%20it%20is%20being%20used%20in%20Phoenix%20to%20understand%20what%20happens%20to%20the%20body%20when%20a%20human%20gets%20heatstroke%20and%20how%20can%20we%20protect%20ourselves%20in%20a%20warming%20planet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20university%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.asu.edu%2F20230525-solutions-meet-andi-worlds-first-outdoor-sweating-breathing-and-walking-manikin%5C%22%3Epublished%20a%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20unique%20robot%20in%20May%20this%20year.%20It%20can%20mimic%20the%20thermal%20functions%20of%20the%20human%20body%20and%20has%2035%20different%20surface%20areas%20that%20are%20all%20individually%20controlled%20with%20temperature%20sensors%2C%20heat%20flux%20sensors%20and%20pores%20that%20bead%20sweat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20the%20world's%20first%20outdoor%20thermal%20mannequin%20that%20we%20can%20routinely%20take%20outside%20and%20...%20measure%20how%20much%20heat%20he%20is%20receiving%20from%20the%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20mechanical%20engineering%20professor%20Konrad%20Rykaczewski%20told%20news%20agency%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20robot%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%20realistic%20way%20to%20experimentally%20measure%20how%20a%20human%20person%20responds%20to%20extreme%20climate%26quot%3B%20without%20putting%20people%20themselves%20at%20risk%2C%20the%20researcher%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20now%2C%20only%20a%20dozen%20or%20so%20mannequins%20of%20this%20type%20existed%2C%20and%20none%20of%20them%20could%20venture%20outdoors.%20But%20this%20ANDI%20is%20only%20one%20of%20two%20used%20by%20research%20institutions%20and%20the%20first%20to%20have%20a%20unique%20internal%20cooling%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArizona's%20capital%20Phoenix%20is%20enduring%20its%20longest%20heat%20wave%20in%20history.%20On%20Friday%2C%20the%20temperature%20exceeded%20110%2043%20degrees%20Celsius%20for%20the%2022nd%20day%20in%20a%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20put%20humans%20in%20dangerous%20extreme%20heat%20situations%20and%20test%20what%20would%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jenni%20Vanos%2C%20associate%20professor%20in%20the%20School%20of%20Sustainability.%20%26quot%3BBut%20there%20are%20situations%20we%20know%20of%20in%20the%20Valley%20where%20people%20are%20dying%20of%20heat%20and%20we%20still%20don't%20fully%20understand%20what%20happened.%20ANDI%20can%20help%20us%20figure%20that%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20ANDI's%20home%2C%20a%20newly%20developed%20heat%20chamber%2C%20researchers%20can%20simulate%20heat-exposure%20scenarios%20from%20different%20places%20around%20the%20globe.%20Here%2C%20temperature%20can%20reach%20up%20to%2060%20degrees%20Celsius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20robot%20has%20internal%20cooling%20channels%20that%20help%20ANDI%20in%20various%20scenarios%20-%20solar%20radiation%20from%20the%20sun%2C%20infrared%20radiation%20from%20the%20ground%20and%20convection%20from%20the%20surrounding%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearchers%20hope%20the%20robot%20will%20provide%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20hyperthermia%20-%20that%20is%2C%20when%20a%20body%20overheats%2C%20a%20condition%20that%20is%20threatening%20a%20growing%20proportion%20of%20the%20world's%20population%20as%20a%20result%20of%20global%20warming.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690194240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fkbvjbct_andi-robot-heat-wave-1200_625x300_24_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frobot-that-can-breathe-and-sweat-helps-scientists-understand-impact-of-soaring-heat-4236324%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20ANDI%20the%20robot's%20home%2C%20a%20newly%20developed%20heat%20chamber%2C%20researchers%20can%20simulate%20heat-exposure%20scenarios%20from%20different%20places%20around%20the%20globe.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%