et%20Nasrulla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20official%20document%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Interior%20sent%20to%20Pakistan's%20High%20Commission%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20the%20chancery%20was%20informed%20that%20it%20had%20been%20decided%20to%20grant%20a%2030-day%20visa%20to%20Anju%2C%20valid%20for%20Upper%20Dir%20only.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENasrullah%2C%20a%20science%20graduate%20from%20a%20University%20in%20Sheringal%2C%20is%20the%20youngest%20among%20five%20brothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20given%20an%20affidavit%20to%20local%20authorities%2C%20stating%20that%20there%20is%20no%20love%20angle%20to%20their%20friendship%2C%20and%20Anju%20will%20return%20to%20India%20on%20August%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20affidavit%20also%20states%20that%20she%20will%20not%20move%20out%20of%20the%20Upper%20Dir%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20will%20definitely%20go%20back%20on%20August%2020%20as%20per%20her%20visa%20documents%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20police%20officer%20Mushtaq.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistrict%20Police%20Officer%20Mushtaq%20interviewed%20Anju%20in%20his%20office%20on%20Sunday%20and%20checked%20her%20travel%20documents%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20which%20a%20no-objection%20certificate%20was%20issued%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENasrullah%20said%20they%20have%20been%20provided%20adequate%20security%20by%20the%20district%20administration%20and%20Anju%20is%20safe%20and%20sound%20with%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20villagers%2C%20mostly%20Pashtuns%20who%20are%20very%20religious%20people%2C%20want%20Anju%20to%20return%20safely%20to%20India%20as%20they%20do%20not%20want%20any%20bad%20name%20for%20their%20community%20due%20to%20this%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnju's%20husband%20Arvind%2C%20who%20is%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20is%20hopeful%20that%20his%20wife%20will%20return%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20a%2015-year-old%20daughter%20and%20a%20six-year-old%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnju's%20incident%20is%20similar%20to%20Seema%20Ghulam%20Haider's%20case.%20Seema%2C%20a%20Pakistani%20mother%20of%20four%2C%20sneaked%20into%20India%20to%20live%20with%20Sachin%20Meena%2C%20a%20Hindu%20man%20she%20got%20in%20touch%20with%20while%20playing%20PUBG%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema%2C%2030%2C%20and%20Sachin%2C%2022%2C%20live%20in%20the%20Rabupura%20area%20of%20Greater%20Noida%2C%20near%20Delhi%2C%20where%20he%20runs%20a%20provision%20store%2C%20according%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Seema%20was%20arrested%20on%20July%204%20for%20illegally%20entering%20India%20without%20a%20visa%20via%20Nepal%20with%20her%20four%20children%2C%20all%20aged%20below%20seven%20years%2C%20Sachin%20was%20put%20behind%20bars%20for%20sheltering%20the%20illegal%20immigrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20unlike%20Seema%20who%20entered%20India%20without%20a%20visa%20via%20Nepal%20with%20her%20four%20children%20all%20aged%20below%20seven%20years%2C%20Anju%20has%20travelled%20to%20Pakistan%20legally%20from%20India%20via%20the%20Wagah-Attari%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnju's%20husband%20Arvind%20told%20the%20media%20in%20Bhiwadi%2C%20Rajasthan%20that%20she%20left%20home%20on%20Thursday%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20going%20to%20Jaipur%20but%20later%20the%20family%20came%20to%20know%20that%20she%20was%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnju's%20husband%20said%20that%20she%20left%20home%20on%20Thursday.%20She%20has%20a%20valid%20passport%2C%E2%80%9D%20Assistant%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Bhiwadi%20Sujit%20Shankar%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20family%20did%20not%20lodge%20a%20complaint%20after%20they%20came%20to%20know%20about%20Anju's%20travel%20to%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20told%20the%20media%20at%20his%20home%20that%20his%20wife%20Anju%20told%20her%20sister%20that%20she%20was%20in%20Lahore%20and%20later%20he%20spoke%20to%20her%20on%20a%20WhatsApp%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20would%20talk%20to%20her%20and%20will%20ask%20her%20to%20return%2C%20asserting%20that%20he%20was%20hopeful%20that%20she%20would%20return%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20her%20passport%20was%20issued%20in%202020%20as%20she%20wanted%20to%20apply%20for%20a%20job%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20said%20he%20had%20no%20idea%20that%20she%20was%20in%20touch%20with%20anyone%20on%20social%20media.%20PTI%20CORR%20SH%20AMS%20MRJ%20AKJ%20AMS%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690193820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F20oglcho_indias-anju-reached-pakistan_625x300_23_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-plans-to-marry-she-will-return-to-india-pak-friend-of-indian-woman-4236238%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20married%20Indian%20woman%20who%20travelled%20legally%20to%20a%20remote%20village%20in%20Pakistan%20to%20meet%20her%20Facebook%20friend%20will%20return%20to%20India%20on%20August%2020%20when%20her%20visa%20expires%2C%20her%20Pakistani%20friend%20said%20on%20Monday%2C%20dismissing%20reports%20of%20any%20love%20angle.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-plans-to-marry-she-will-return-to-india-pak-friend-of-indian-woman-4236238%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-plans-to-marry-she-will-return-to-india-pak-friend-of-indian-woman-4236238%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-plans-to-marry-she-will-return-to-india-pak-friend-of-indian-woman-4236238%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dhindora%20song%3A%20Ranveer-Alia%20are%20rebels%20in%20love%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690193528000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.to