rder%20from%20the%20leader%20of%20Sikhism%E2%80%99s%20highest%20temporal%20seat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHarjinder%20Singh%20Dhami%2C%20the%20SGPC%E2%80%99s%20chief%2C%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Tribune%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20it%20is%20working%20to%20set%20up%20its%20channel.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20started%20the%20process%20to%20acquire%20equipment%20and%20permission%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting.%20It%20may%20take%20two%20%5Bto%5D%20three%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20YouTube%20channel%20will%20broadcast%20the%20Sikh%20rituals%20in%20three%20blocks%20%E2%80%93%20one%20from%203%3A30%20am%20to%208%3A30%20am%2C%20one%20from%2012%3A30%20pm%20to%202%3A30%20pm%2C%20and%20the%20final%20one%20from%206%3A30%20pm%20to%208%3A30%20pm%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Tribune%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SGPC%20is%20the%20apex%20organisation%20responsible%20for%20the%20management%20of%20gurdwaras%20in%20India.%20It%20manages%20the%20Golden%20Temple%2C%20which%20is%20the%20holiest%20Sikh%20shrine%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20SGPC%20clarified%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIE%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20rituals%E2%80%99%20broadcast%20rights%20have%20been%20transferred%20to%20itself%20from%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPTC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24141536%2FSGPC-press-1024x512.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%