0Gurdwaras%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMann%E2%80%99s%20comments%20are%20linked%20to%20the%20belief%20of%20his%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20cadre%20in%20Punjab%20%E2%80%93%20which%20also%20leads%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20government%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20broadcast%20of%20these%20rituals%20must%20be%20made%20freely%20available%20and%20not%20be%20under%20the%20monopoly%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPTC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20charge%20against%20the%20%E2%80%98Badals%E2%80%99%20refers%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Badal%20family%2C%20an%20influential%20political%20family%20that%20Sukhbir%20Singh%20Badal%2C%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20party%2C%20is%20part%20of.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBadal%20reportedly%20has%20a%20stake%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPTC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%2085vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F11160722%2FFXXbD1XaAAEdRPF-300x168.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F11160722%2FFXXbD1XaAAEdRPF-300x168.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F11160722%2FFXXbD1XaAAEdRPF.jpeg%20739w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-606954%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22168%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPunjab%20CM%20Bhagwant%20Mann.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40AAPPunjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20pursuance%20of%20their%20goal%2C%20the%20AAP-led%20government%20passed%20the%20Sikh%20Gurdwaras%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%20through%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20legislative%20assembly%20in%20June%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bill%20seeks%20to%20add%20a%20clause%20to%20the%20Sikh%20Gurdwaras%20Act%2C%201925%2C%20which%20stipulates%20that%20the%20SGPC%20should%20propagate%20the%20%E2%80%9Cteachings%20of%20the%20Gurus%20uninterrupted%20(without%20any%20on-screen%20advertisements%2C%20commercials%20or%20distortion)%20live%20feed%20of%20gurbani%20from%20the%20Golden%20Temple%2C%20Amritsar%20every%20day%20available%20free%20of%20cost%20to%20all%20media%20houses%2C%20platforms%2C%20channels%20or%20whoever%20wishes%20to%20broadcast%20it%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20met%20with%20criticism%20from%20the%20SGPC%2C%20which%20says%20that%20the%20legislation%20amounts%20to%20interference%20with%20Sikh%20religious%20matters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20SGPC%20has%20its%20own%20constitution%2C%20executive%20body%20and%20as%20per%20agreement%2C%20nobody%20can%20interfere%20in%20its%20functioning.%20But%20Mann%20overlooked%20all%20these%20facts%20and%20meddled%20with%20the%20SGPC%E2%80%99s%20affairs%2C%E2%80%9D%20former%20SGPC%20president%20Bibi%20Jagir%20Kaur%20previously%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPal%20Singh%20Nauli%2C%20a%20senior%20Punjab-based%20journalist%2C%20also%20spoke%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20about%20the%20dubious%20nature%20of%20the%20amendments%20to%20the%201925%20Act.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20two-thirds%20majority%20of%20the%20SGPC%20is%20mandatory%20for%20any%20kind%20of%20amendment%20in%20the%201925%20Act.%20But%20this%20fact%20was%20ignored.%20Given%20the%20kind%20of%20resistance%20the%20Gurdwara%20Amendment%20Bill%20was%20facing%2C%20it%20should%20not%20get%20the%20governor%E2%80%99s%20assent.%20However%2C%20in%20case%20it%20gets%20the%20nod%2C%20the%20Bill%20will%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20the%20government%20to%20fulfil%20its%20hidden%20agenda%20in%20the%20SGPC%E2%80%99s%20functioning%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fexplained-controversy-bill-amend-sikh-gurdwaras-act%5C%22%3EExplained%3A%20The%20Controversy%20Around%20a%20Bill%20to%20Amend%20the%20Sikh%20Gurdwaras%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20addressing%20the%20media%20about%20the%20SGPC%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20stream%20the%20gurbani%20and%20kirtan%2C%20Dhami%20asked%20the%20Punjab%20government%20not%20to%20interfere%20in%20its%20affairs%20and%20that%20the%20Sikh%20community%20knows%20how%20to%20handle%20its%20own%20affairs%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bill%20will%20need%20the%20Punjab%20governor%E2%80%99s%20assent%20in%20order%20to%20proceed%20into%20enactment.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20governor%20Banwari%20Lal%20Purohit%20refused%20to%20assent%20to%20the%20Gurdwara%20Amendment%20Bill%20as%20well%20as%20four%20other%20Bills%20the%20assembly%20passed%20last%20month.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20the%20assembly%E2%80%99s%20special%20two-day%20session%20on%20June%2019%20and%2020%20were%20possibly%20illegal%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fcities%2Fchandigarh%2Fstory%2Fpunjab-governor-says-recent-assembly-session-breached-law-bills-passed-illegaly-2408284-2023-07-18%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20chief%20minister%2C%20you%20will%20appreciate%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Punjab%20are%20equally%20concerned%20with%20ensuring%20that%20laws%20that%20ultimately%20affect%20them%20are%20passed%20after%20following%20due%20procedure.%20You%20may%20rest%20assured%20that%20I%20shall%20take%20action%20according%20to%20the%20law%20after%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20session%20is%20first%20examined%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20to%20Mann%20according%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20said%20that%20Purohit%E2%80%99s%20actions%20%E2%80%9C%5Bstifled%5D%20the%20democratic%20will%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Punjab.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690193449000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F19174310%2FSarovar_and_the_Golden_Temple.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fsgpc-begins-livestreaming-golden-temple-rituals-on-youtube%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Shiromani%20Gurdwara%20Parbandhak%20Committee's%20decision%20comes%20days%20after%20the%20Punjab%20governor%20refused%20to%20assent%20to%20the%20Bhagwant%20Mann-led%20controversial%20Sikh%20Gurdwaras%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fsgpc-begins-livestreaming-golden-temple-rituals-on-youtube%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cambodia%E2%80%99s%20Hun%20Sen%20Sets%20Stage%20for%20Son%E2%80%99s%20Succession%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24153206%2Fhun-sen.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ECambodia%20went%20to%20the%20polls%20on%20Sunday%20with%20the%20incumbent%20Prime%20Minister%20Hun%20Sen%20guaranteed%20to%20win%20after%20effectively%20suppressing%20all%20forms%20of%20dissent%20and%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vote%20marked%C2%A0a%20once-in-a-generation%20leadership%20transition%C2%A0in%20which%20the%20long-ruling%20Cambodian%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%20(CPP)%20is%20expected%20to%20seal%C2%A0a%20clean%20sweep%20of%20parliamentary%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20CPP%E2%80%99s%20main%20challenger%20was%20barred%20from%20competing%20in%20the%20vote%20on%20a%20registration%20technicality%2C%20many%20analysts%20say%20that%20the%20one-sided%20ballot%20will%20be%20used%20as%20a%20plebiscite%20on%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fcambodia-hun-sen-holds-control-of-media-ahead-of-election%2Fa-66203311%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Hun%20Sen%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0plans%20to%20hand%20over%20power%20to%20his%20eldest%20son%2C%20Hun%20Manet%2C%20who%20head%E2%80%99s%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20possible%20that%20before%20late%20August%2C%20a%20leadership%20reshuffle%20could%20see%20almost%20the%20entire%20cabinet%20replaced%20by%20younger%20officials%2C%20mostly%20the%20children%20or%20relatives%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20aging%20grandees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20pundits%20reckon%20that%20Hun%20Sen%E2%80%99s%20handover%20of%20the%20premiership%20could%20take%20place%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGenerational%20succession%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPP%20first%20took%20power%20in%201979%20after%20a%20group%20of%20Khmer%20Rouge%20defectors%2C%20including%20Hun%20Sen%2C%20returned%20alongside%20the%20Vietnamese%20military%20to%20overthrow%20the%20genocidal%20regime.%20Hun%20Sen%20was%20made%20prime%20minister%20in%201985%2C%20making%20him%20currently%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20longest-ruling%20head%20of%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20well%20as%20Hun%20Manet%20inheriting%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20premiership%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20expected%20that%20the%20sons%20of%20the%20powerful%20interior%20minister%2C%20Sar%20Kheng%2C%20and%C2%A0Defense%20Minister%20Tea%20Banh%20will%20also%20inherit%20their%20fathers%E2%80%99%20offices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUp%20to%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20cabinet%2C%20known%20as%20the%20Council%20of%20Ministers%2C%C2%A0could%20make%20way%20for%20younger%20officials%2C%20while%20the%20numerous%20deputy%20prime%20ministers%20and%20ministers%20without%20portfolio%20will%20also%20be%20reshuffled%2C%20according%20to%20internal%20nominee%20lists%20leaked%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20could%20thus%20lead%20to%20a%20repeat%20of%20history.%20At%20the%20last%20general%20election%20in%202018%2C%20the%20CPP%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fcambodia-hun-sen-sweeps-all-in-election-result%2Fa-45096365%5C%22%3Ewon%20all%20125%20parliamentary%20seats%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0after%20having%20forcibly%20dissolved%20its%20main%20rival%20at%20the%20time.%20The%20Cambodia%20National%20Rescue%20Party%20(CNRP)%20was%20banned%20over%20the%20spurious%20accusation%20of%20plotting%20a%20US-backed%20coup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%20this%20year%2C%20following%20months%20of%20intimidation%20of%20its%20senior%20members%2C%20the%20CPP%E2%80%99s%20only%20credible%20rival%2C%20the%20Candlelight%20Party%2C%20was%20barred%20from%20competing%20in%20Sunday%E2%80%99s%20election%20because%20of%20a%20paperwork%20dispute%20%E2%80%94%20a%20ruling%20that%20Amnesty%20International%20said%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpolitically%20motivated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Candlelight%20Party%20%E2%80%94%20which%C2%A0won%2022%25%20of%20the%20popular%20vote%20at%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20local%20elections%20%E2%80%94%20claimed%20this%20was%20a%20trumped-up%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20year%2C%20the%20authorities%20have%20closed%20independent%20news%20outlets%2C%20jailed%20numerous%20opposition%20activists%20and%20critics%2C%20and%20instigated%20loyalty%20tests%20across%20all%20of%20society.%20By%20one%20estimate%2C%20more%20than%206%2C000%20members%20of%20opposition%20parties%20have%20defected%20to%20the%20CPP%20%E2%80%94%20either%20out%20of%20fear%2C%20financial%20incentives%20or%20a%20desire%20for%20a%20quiet%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20upcoming%20election%20bears%20little%20resemblance%20to%20an%20actual%20democratic%20process%2C%E2%