red%20for%20the%20final%20by%20watching%20videos%20of%20Indian%20batters%2C%20including%20key%20players%20Sai%20Sudarshan%20and%20Abhishek%20Sharma%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20title%20clash.%C2%A0Tayyab%20Tahir's%20heroics%20with%20the%20bat%20and%20Sufiyan%20Muqeem's%20efforts%20with%20the%20ball%20took%20Paksitan%20A%20across%20the%20finish%20line%20against%20India%20A%20in%20an%20encounter%20that%20was%20one-sided%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20game%20in%20the%20final%20of%20the%20ACC%20Men's%20Emerging%20Teams%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20on%20Sunday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirstly%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20congratulate%20all%20of%20Pakistan.%20This%20is%20what%20happens%2C%20when%20you%20score%20big%20runs%20in%20a%20final%2C%20the%20opposition%20comes%20under%20pressure%20and%20then%20if%20you%20get%20back-to-back%20wickets%20it%20gets%20tough%20for%20them.%20We%20had%20tried%20different%20combinations%20in%20the%20last%20four-five%20matches%2C%20tried%20different%20players%2C%20and%20it%20worked%20well%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Haris%20in%20the%20post-match%20presentation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20shown%20the%20videos%20of%20the%20Indian%20batters%20to%20our%20bowlers.%20Sai%20Sudharsan%20and%20Abhishek%20were%20their%20main%20players%20and%20we%20thought%20that%20if%20we%20could%20get%20them%20out%20early%2C%20it%20would%20help%20us.%20I%20am%20very%20happy%20with%20how%20the%20boys%20are%20motivated.%20We%20have%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20also%20coming%20up%20and%20the%20World%20Cup%20too%20after%20that.%20Sri%20Lanka%20is%20a%20tough%20place%20to%20play%20spin.%20So%20it%20was%20good%20preparation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20India%20opted%20to%20field%20first%20after%20winning%20the%20toss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20put%20up%20352%2F8%20in%20their%2050%20overs.%20Saim%20Ayub%20(59%20in%2051%20balls%2C%20with%20seven%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes)%20and%20Sahibzada%20Farhan%20(65%20in%2062%20balls%20with%20four%20boundaries%20and%20sixes%20each)%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20a%20massive%20total%20following%20a%20121-run%20opening%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20their%20dismissal%2C%20Pakistan%20A%20sunk%20to%20187%2F5%2C%20but%20Tayyab%20Tahir%20changed%20the%20game%20from%20that%20point.%20He%20put%20on%20a%20126-run%20partnership%20for%20the%20sixth%20wicket%20with%20Mubasir%20Khan%20(35%20in%2047%20balls)%2C%20which%20took%20Pakistan%20beyond%20300%20runs.%20Tayyab%20smashed%20108%20in%20just%2071%20balls%2C%20with%2012%20fours%20and%20four%20sixes.%20This%20knock%20powered%20Pakistan%20to%20a%20huge%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERiyan%20Parag%20(2%2F24)%20and%20Rajvardhan%20Hangargekar%20(2%2F48)%20took%20two%20wickets%20each.%20Manav%20Suthar%2C%20Nishant%20Sandhu%20and%20Harshit%20Rana%20got%20one%20wicket%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20chase%20of%20353%2C%20India%20responded%20with%20a%20quickfire%2064-run%20opening%20stand%20between%20Sai%20Sudarshan%20(29)%20and%20Abhishek%20Sharma.%20After%20Nikin%20Jose%20(11)%20departed%20early%2C%20Abhishek%20had%20a%2052-run%20third-wicket%20partnership%20with%20skipper%20Yash%20(39%20in%2041%20balls).%20Following%20Abhishek's%20dismissal%20for%2061%20off%2051%20balls%2C%20consisting%20of%20five%20fours%20and%20a%20six%2C%20India%20could%20not%20make%20a%20comeback%20in%20the%20match%20and%20were%20bundled%20out%20for%20224%20runs%20in%2040%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESufiyan%20Muqeem%20(3%2F66)%20was%20the%20pick%20of%20the%20bowlers%20for%20Pakistan%2C%20while%20Arshad%20Iqbal%2C%20Mehran%20Mumtaz%20and%20Mohammed%20Wasim%20also%20got%20two%20wickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETayyab%20earned%20the%20'Player%20of%20the%20Match'%20for%20his%20knock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690192320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fbco4dc28_mohammad-haris_625x300_24_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwatched-videos-of-pakistan-a-skipper-reveals-masterplan-that-aced-india-a-test-in-final-4235030%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan%20A%20skipper%20Mohammad%20Haris%20said%20that%20his%20team%20prepared%20for%20the%20final%20by%20watching%20videos%20of%20Indian%20batters%2C%20including%20key%20players%20Sai%20Sudarshan%20and%20Abhishek%20Sharma%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20title%20clash.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A43%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwatched-videos-of-pakistan-a-skipper-reveals-masterplan-that-aced-india-a-test-in-final-4235030%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwatched-videos-of-pakistan-a-skipper-reveals-masterplan-that-aced-india-a-test-in-final-4235030%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwatched-videos-of-pakistan-a-skipper-reveals-masterplan-that-aced-india-a-test-in-final-4235030%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20SpaceX%20Rocket%20Punches%20Hole%20In%20Ionosphere%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20rocket%20launched%20by%20Elon%20Musk's%20SpaceX%20punched%20a%20temporary%20hole%20in%20the%20ionosphere%20surrounding%20our%20planet%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3Espaceweather.com%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20Falcon%209%20rocket%20was%20launched%20on%20July%2019%20from%20the%20Vandenberg%20Space%20Force%20Base%20in%20California.%20According%20to%20the%20company%20website%2C%20it%20is%20a%20reusable%2C%20two-stage%20rocket%20for%20the%20reliable%20and%20safe%20transport%20of%20people%20and%20payloads%20into%20Earth%20orbit%20and%20beyond.%20SpaceX%20also%20said%20that%20it%20is%20the%20world's%20first%20orbital%20class%20reusable%20rocket.%20Falcon%209%20has%20conducted%20240%20launches%20and%20198%20landings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhotos%20from%20the%20July%2019%20launch%20showed%20a%20faint%20red%20glow%2C%20which%20was%20studied%20by%20space%20physicist%20Jeff%20Baumgardner%20from%20Boston%20University.%20After%20reviewed%20the%20footage%20of%20the%20launch%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20red%20glow%20indicates%20that%20a%20hole%20was%20made%20in%20the%20ionosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20well-studied%20phenomenon%20when%20rockets%20are%20burning%20their%20engines%20200%20to%20300%20km%20above%20Earth's%20surface%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Baumgardner%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspaceweatherarchive.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Espaceweather.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20reviewed%20footage%20from%20the%20July%2019th%20launch.%20It%20shows%20the%20second%20stage%20engine%20burning%20at%20286%20km%20near%20the%20F-region%20peak%20for%20that%20time%20of%20day.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20quite%20possible%20that%20an%20ionospheric%20'hole'%20was%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ionosphere%20lies%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20space%20and%20is%20filled%20with%20charged%20particles%20called%20ions.%20According%20to%20NASA%2C%20it%20is%20the%20reason%20that%20geomagnetic%20storms%20cause%20aurora%2C%20with%20solar%20plasma%20reacting%20with%20the%20ions%20to%20create%20the%20spectacular%20colours%20seen%20in%20the%20sky.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20event%20involving%20the%20same%20rocket%20happened%20earlier%20too.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencetimes.com%2Farticles%2F45009%2F20230722%2Fspacex-falcon-9-rocket-temporary-hole-ionosphere-elon-musk.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EScience%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Falcon%209%20was%20launched%20from%20Vanderberg%20Space%20Force%20Base%20carrying%20FORMOSAT-5%20payload%20on%20August%2024%2C%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20low%20weight%2C%20the%20rocket%20launched%20along%20a%20vertical%20path%20rather%20than%20travelling%20parallel%20to%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20Earth%2C%20creating%20shockwaves.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20it%20ruptured%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20plasma%20of%20the%20ionosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20thing%20happened%20again%20when%20the%20Falcon%209%20rocket%20was%20launched%20on%20June%2019%2C%202022%2C%20the%20outlet%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690192200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-02%2Fd15ia4g8_spacex-falcon-9-rocket-afp_625x300_10_February_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musks-spacex-rocket-punches-hole-in-ionosphere-4236181%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ionosphere%20lies%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20space%20and%20is%20filled%20with%20charged%20particles%20called%20ions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musks-spacex-rocket-punches-hole-in-ionosphere-4236181%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musks-spacex-rocket-punches-hole-in-ionosphere-4236181%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musks-spacex-rocket-punches-hole-in-ionosphere-4236181%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amit%20Shah%20Says%20%5C%22Ready%20For%20Manipur%20Discussion%5C%22%2C%20Takes%20A%20Swipe%20At%20Opposition%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20Opposition%20protests%20over%20the%20horrifying%20video%20of%20a%20mob%20parading%20two%20Manipur%20women%20naked%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20today%20said%20he%20is%20ready%20for%20a%20discussion%20and%20asked%20why%20the%20Opposition%20is%20not%20cooperating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20Monsoon%20Session%20of%20Parliament%20began%20on%20a%20stormy%20note%20over%20the%20shocking%20video%20from%20the%20northeastern%20state%2C%20the%20Opposition%20has%20been%20demanding%20a%20discussion.%20The%20centre%20has%20maintained%20that%20it%20is%20ready%20to%20discuss%20the%20matter.%20Earlier%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20that%20the%20centre%20is%20prepared%20to%20talk%20on%20the%20sensitive%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20brief%20address%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20urged%20Opposition%20leaders%20to%20allow%20a%20debate%20on%20the%20issue.%20He%20said%20it%20was%20important%20for%20the%20truth%20in%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20to%20come%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Minister%20made%20the%20remarks%20after%20the%20House%20was%20adjourned%20thrice%20over%20the%20Manipur%20situation.%20When%20the%20House%20met%20at%202.30%20pm%2C%20he%20said%20MPs%20from%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20political%20aisle%20want%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20issue.%20The%20Opposition%20MPs%2C%20however%2C%20continued%20the%20protest%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20adjourned%20the%20proceedings%20for%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Parliament%20met%20for%20the%20Monsoon%20Session%20Thursday%2C%20at%20least%2015%20Opposition%20MPs%20moved%20adjournment%20notices%2C%20seeking%20a%20discussion%20on%20situation%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state%20where%20ethnic%20violence%20has%20claimed%20more%20than%20a%20100%20lives%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months.%20The%20centre%20agreed%20to%20discuss%20the%20matter%20but%20chaos%20erupted%20over%20a%20technicality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20MPs%20wanted%20that%20the%20matter%20be%20discussed%20under%20Rule%20267.%20Under%20this%20rule%2C%20all%20business%20in%20the%20House%20is%20suspended%20and%20a%20specific%20matter%20is%20discussed.%20In%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%2027%20MPs%20had%20submitted%20notices%20to%20raise%20a%20discussion%20under%20Rule%20267.%20The%20Centre%2C%20however%2C%20was%20only%20ready%20for%20a%20discussion%20under%20Rule%20176%2C%20which%20provides%20for%20a%20short%20duration%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountering%20the%20Opposition's%20charge%20on%20the%20sexual%20assault%20of%20women%20in%20Manipur%2C%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20has%20said%20atrocities%20of%20women%20across%20all%20states%2C%20including%20the%20Opposition-ruled%20Rajasthan%20and%20West%20Bengal%2C%20need%20to%20be%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690192140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fpfrq07p4_amit-shah-_625x300_24_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famit-shah-says-ready-for-manipur-discussion-takes-a-swipe-at-opposition-4236080%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20Opposition%20protests%20over%20the%20horrifying%20video%20of%20a%20mob%20parading%20two%20Manipur%20women%20naked%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20today%20said%20he%20is%20ready%20for%20a%20discussion%20and%20asked%20why%20the%20Opposition%20is%20not%20cooperating.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famit-shah-says-ready-for-manipur-discussion-takes-a-swipe-at-opposition-4236080%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famit-shah-says-ready-for-manipur-discussion-takes-a-swipe-at-opposition-4236080%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famit-shah-says-ready-for-manipur-discussion-takes-a-swipe-at-opposition-4236080%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Greta%20Thunberg%20fined%20for%20disobeying%20police%20order%20at%20protest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690192140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F07%2F1600x900%2Fskynews-greta-thunberg-malmo_6228711.jpg%3F20230724113212%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fgreta-thunberg-arrives-at-swedish-court-after-being-charged-with-disobeying-police-at-protest-12926537%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Greta%20Thunberg%20has%20been%20fined%20after%20being%20charged%20with