atforms%2C%20state%20functionaries%2C%20local%20politicians%2C%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20were%20all%20almost%20compelled%20to%20break%20their%20silence.%20But%20this%20came%20after%20almost%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fseventy-nine-days-after-violence-broke-out-narendra-modi-finally-talks-about-manipur%5C%22%3E80%20days%20of%20apathetic%20silence%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20across%20the%20state%20and%20the%20North%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20anger%20from%20state%20officials%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20narrative-management%20agency%20so%20far%20has%20been%20directed%20more%20at%20the%20fact%20on%20how%20the%20news%20of%20violence%20came%20out%20%E2%80%93%20or%20how%20the%20opposition%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20address%20issues%20of%20violence%20against%20women%20in%20their%20own%20states%20%E2%80%93%20as%20against%20resolving%20the%20current%20crisis%20in%20Manipur%20for%20which%20the%20home%20minister%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20his%20government%20can%20be%20held%20directly%20responsible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnsurprisingly%2C%20in%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fseventy-nine-days-after-violence-broke-out-narendra-modi-finally-talks-about-manipur%5C%22%3Espeech%3C%2Fa%3E%20outside%20the%20parliament%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20not%20only%20strategically%20avoided%20taking%20accountability%2C%20or%20accepting%20responsibility%20for%20what%20has%20happened%20over%20the%20last%20two%20months%2C%20he%20left%20his%20remarks%20on%20calling%20the%20incident%20%E2%80%98shameful%E2%80%99.%20Jahnavi%20Sen%20and%20Soumashree%20Sarkar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-talked-about-the-manipur-violence-but-did-he-really%5C%22%3Erecently%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20what%20else%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20failed%20to%20acknowledge%20or%20address%20in%20what%20he%20spoke.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20remarks%2C%20what%20was%20worse%20to%20see%20is%20Modi%20adopting%20the%20role%20of%20a%20patronising%20patriarch%20mentioning%20what%20happened%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98daughters%E2%80%99%20of%20Manipur%20can%20never%20be%20forgiven.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20team%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fswabhimaannetin.wordpress.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESwabhimaan%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20New%20Economics%20Studies%20(CNES)%20at%20O.P.%20Jindal%20Global%20University%2C%20provided%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fbig-talk-small-action-modi-govts-work-on-womens-empowerment-in-the-last-9-years%5C%22%3Ecritique%20of%20nine%20years%20of%20Modi-BJP%20rule%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20its%20performance%20on%20various%20indicators%20such%20as%20women%20safety%2C%20economic%20participation%20for%20women%2C%20and%20social%20opportunities%20for%20women%20(healthcare%20and%20food%20security).%20The%20article%20was%20written%20after%20the%20women%20wrestlers%20were%20manhandled%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Delhi%20while%20protesting%20against%20BJP%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%2C%20against%20whom%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fsport-others%2Fwrestlers-police-complaint-brij-bhushan-sharan-singh-sexual-harassment-8571598%2F%5C%22%3Eseven%20women%20wrestlers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fminor-wrestler-changed-statement-because-her-family-was-threatened-sakshi-malik%5C%22%3Eminor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20made%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20granted%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbail-wfi-chief-brij-bhushan-singh-wrestlers-sexual-harassment-case%5C%22%3Ehim%20bail%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20neither%20supported%20nor%20denied%20the%20bail%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20widening%20gap%20between%20%E2%80%98promises%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98reality%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20appears%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fclient%3Dsafari%26rls%3Den%26q%3Dnyaya%2Band%2Bniti%2Bdeepanshu%2Bmohan%2Bjustice%26ie%3DUTF-8%26oe%3DUTF-8%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMhatsya-Nyaya%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(majoritarian%20justice)%20outlook%20of%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP%20government%20remains%20tightly%20secured%20by%20a%20rule%20anchored%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fclient%3Dsafari%26rls%3Den%26q%3Dnyaya%2Band%2Bniti%2Bdeepanshu%2Bmohan%2Bjustice%26ie%3DUTF-8%26oe%3DUTF-8%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EShakti%20Ki%20Gita%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(rule%20by%20law)%20and%20not%20one%20that%20safeguards%20or%20practises%20any%20rule%20of%20law.%20It%20protects%20those%20in%20power%20no%20matter%20what.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20goes%20without%20saying%20how%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20failed%20miserably%20in%20various%20areas%20of%20economic%20performance%20ranging%20from%20safety%2C%20law%20and%20order%20to%20access%20to%20nutrition%2C%20reproductive%20rights%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20marked%20difference%20in%20this%20government%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Ekathni%3C%2Fem%3E%20(words)%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekarni%3C%2Fem%3E%20(actions).%20The%20ever-widening%20gulf%20between%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjobs-justice-and-smart-cities-the-promises-bjp-made-in-its-2014-manifesto%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98promises%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98reality%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20its%20own%20poll%20promises%20(in%20its%20manifesto)%20%E2%80%93%20is%20scarring%20the%20republic%20that%20was%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%E2%80%99s%20conflict%20and%20reported%20instances%20of%20violence%20against%20women%20%E2%80%93%20amid%20everything%20else%20%E2%80%93%20also%20reflect%20a%20state%20of%20permanence%20in%20the%20regression%20of%20moral%20and%20public%20institutional%20functioning%20that%20operates%20in%20the%20dark%20while%20observing%20a%20culture%20of%20apathetic%20silence.%20This%20is%20the%20unfortunate%20reality%20of%20%E2%80%98New%20India%E2%80%99%20where%20no%20one%E2%80%99s%20pain%20and%20experience%20of%20suffering%20really%20matters%20to%20those%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20how%20well%20India%20is%20positioned%20in%20terms%20of%20its%20foreign%20policy%2C%20or%20how%20well%20the%20nation%20does%20in%20terms%20of%20trade%2C%20or%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20bilateral%20meetings%20Modi%20is%20seen%20celebrating%2C%20when%20its%20own%20domestic%20terrain%20remains%20marred%20by%20daily%20attacks%20against%20its%20citizens%2C%20especially%20women%20and%20children.%20Additionally%2C%20these%20issues%20are%20coupled%20with%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20regimes%20to%20do%20anything%20purposeful%20to%20resolve%20these%20crises%2C%20as%20against%20spending%20more%20resources%20and%20state-capacity%20to%20manage%20or%20control%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnarrative%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHindutva%E2%80%99s%20patriarchal-patronising%20position%20on%20Indian%20women%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20nation%20where%20%E2%80%98Bharat%20Mata%E2%80%99%20is%20pictorially%20represented%20as%20a%20flesh-and-blood%20sari-clad%20Indian%20woman%2C%20a%20naked%20parade%20is%20what%20ignites%20a%20revolution.%20When%20women%20strip%20the%20generationally%20constructed%20idea%20of%20femininity%20and%20chastity%2C%20the%20body%20that%20has%20been%20the%20site%20for%20the%20exertion%20of%20patriarchal%20power%20transforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20an%20isolated%20incident%20as%20casually%20remarked%20by%20Manipur%20chief%20minister%20Biren%20Singh%20%E2%80%93%20who%20asked%20the%20people%20to%20not%20listen%20to%20the%20allegations%20but%20to%20look%20at%20the%20ground%20reality%2C%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-video-arrest-biren-singh-supreme-court%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Chundreds%20of%20similar%20incidents%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20taken%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20in%20Manipur%20have%20been%20facing%20the%20brute%20of%20structural%20violence%20since%20pre-independence%2C%20but%20the%20government%20has%20focussed%20solely%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98security%20issue%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20state%20and%20prioritised%20excessive%20securitisation%20that%20has%20historically%20led%20to%20women%E2%80%99s%20bodies%20transforming%20into%20sights%20of%20violence%20and%20their%20rights%20being%20pushed%20far%20behind%20the%20agendas%20of%20the%20government%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survivors%20of%20the%20incident%20are%20termed%20as%20%E2%80%98daughters%E2%80%99%20only%20because%20they%20are%20under%20the%20control%20of%20the%20patriarch%2C%20which%20in%20this%20case%20is%20the%20state.%20There%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20link%20the%20violation%20of%20their%20bodies%20to%20the%20violation%20of%20the%20state%20and%20hence%20there%20is%20an%20outrage%20and%20call%20for%20their%20honour%20and%20morality%20to%20be%20restored.%20The%20women%20are%20denied%20agency%20and%20are%20never%20seen%20as%20their%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fmanipur-video-kuki-women-stripped-manorama-bilkis-bano%5C%22%3EManipur%20Video%3A%20What%20Connects%203%20Kuki%20Women%20Stripped%2C%20Paraded%20Naked%20to%20Manorama%20and%20Bilkis%20Bano%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELong%20lineage%20of%20structural%20violence%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20anxieties%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Brahmanical%20patriarchal%20society%20is%20found%20in%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fare-we-allowing-fathers-to-be-equal-parents%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520answer%2520is%253A%2520No%252C%2520they%2Cto%2520not%2520be%2520involved%2520fathers.%5C%22%3E%20idea%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20where%20motherhood%20is%20a%20biological%20fact%2C%20fatherhood%20is%20a%20sociological%20fiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20leads%20to%20stringent%20regulation%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20sexuality%20to%20maintain%20the%20existing%20hegemonies.%20The%20concept%20of%20structural%20violence%20was%20brought%20about%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC5561688%2F%5C%22%3EJohan%20Galtung%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%201969%2C%20who%20referredi%20to%20a%20type%20of%20violence%20where%20a%20social%20structure%20or%20social%20organisation%20may%20cause%20harm%20to%20people%20by%20preventing%20them%20from%20satisfying%20their%20basic%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUndoubtedly%2C%20women%20and%20gender-variant%20persons%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20have%20historically%20faced%20double%20marginalisation%20from%20the%20state%20that%20takes%20the%20role%20of%20the%20patriarch%2C%20and%20the%20patriarchal%20structures%20that%20exist%20within%20their%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20language%20of%20rights%20is%20predominantly%20masculine%20in%20Manipur%2C%20as%20it%20primarily%20emphasises%20security-related%20rights.%20Instead%20of%20focusing%20on%20individual%20lives%2C%20the%20masculine%20state%20views%20security%20as%20safeguarding%20the%20country%20and%20its%20borders%20from%20outside%20threats%20or%20internal%20conflicts.%20This%20leads%20to%20the%20invisibilisation%20of%20women%20in%20the%20state%20who%20have%20been%20harbingers%20of%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20one%20talks%20about%20the%20movement%20of%20women%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Nupi%20Lan%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20which%20were%20demonstrations%20against%20the%20direct%20colonial%20rule%20and%20policies%20that%20affected%20their%20economic%20standpoint%20in%201939%20%E2%80%93%20or%20the%20naked%20protest%20of%2012%20%3Cem%3Eimas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(mothers)%20in%20front%20of%20the%20headquarters%20of%20Assam%20Rifles%20against%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%2032-year-old%20woman%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thepolisproject.com%2Fread%2Fmanipurs-long-wait-for-justice-remembering-1528-cases-and-the-murder-of-thangjam-manorama%2F%5C%22%3EManorama%20Thangjam%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20committed%20by%20the%20paramilitary%20soldiers%2C%20women%20have%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20violence%20and%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20that%2C%20as%20Shreema%20Ningombam%20rightfully%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.humanrights.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2Ftraditional-and-militarized-society.pdf%5C%22%3E%20puts%20forth%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20Manipur%2C%20there%20are%20many%20instances%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20issues%20being%20consumed%20by%20the%20flames%20of%20nationalist%20politics%2C%20under%20the%20premise%20that%20the%20resolution%20of%20the%20conflict%20and%20ethnic%20tensions%20is%20more%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKey%20issues%20of%20concern%20to%20women%20include%20domestic%20violence%2C%20marital%20rape%2C%20sexual%20abuse%2C%20suicide%2C%20murder%2C%20and%20widows%E2%80%99%20plight%20within%20the%20family%2C%20as%20well%20as%20reproductive%20rights%2C%20bodily%20autonomy%2C%20property%20rights%2C%20legal%20rights%2C%20medical%20rights%2C%20media%20and%20cultural%20representation%2C%20women%20trafficking%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20taboos%20and%20stigmas%2C%20moral%20policing%2C%20female%20foeticide.%20These%2C%20together%20with%20the%20issues%20of%20education%2C%20health%2C%20and%20governance%20in%20Manipur%2C%20have%20been%20subsumed%20by%20the%20political%20tussle%20between%20the%20armed%20opposition%20and%20the%20state%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20politicisation%20of%20ethnicity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-many-inversions-of-justice-and-accountability-in-manipur%5C%22%3EThe%20Many%20Inversions%20of%20Justice%20and%20Accountability%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20impact%20of%20intersectionality%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntersectionality%20is%20a%20crucial%20analytical%20tool%20for%20acknowledging%20that%20each%20person%20has%20interconnected%20identities%20and%20experiences%2C%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20first%20steps%20toward%20effectively%20understanding%20the%20layers%20of%20marginalisation%20and%20discrimination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20%E2%80%98intersectionality%E2%80%99%20can%20be%20traced%20back%20to%20Crenshaw%20(1991)%2C%20who%20saw%20it%20as%20a%20method%20for%20addressing%20tendencies%20of%20identity%20politics%20to%20disregard%20and%20homogenise%20intragroup%20differences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20analysing%20violence%20against%20women%2C%20which%20she%20claimed%20was%20%E2%80%9Coften%20shaped%20by%20other%20dimensions%20of%20identities%2C%20such%20as%20race%20and%20class%2C%E2%80%9D%20Crenshaw%20considered%20this%20to%20be%20particularly%20problematic%20since%20it%20not%20only%20obscures%20the%20causes%20and%20experiences%20of%20violence%20against%20women%20but%20also%20makes%20the%20politicisation%20of%20violence%20more%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Bharat%20H.%20Desai%20and%20Balraj%20K.%20Sidhu%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fjournal%2F2017%2F7%2Fcommentary%2Fsexual-violence-conflict-zones.html%5C%22%3Enoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20pre-existing%20exclusions%20and%20prejudice%20that%20are%20typical%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20status%20in%20many%20countries%20exacerbate%20the%20battle%20to%20provide%20justice%20for%20women%20victims%20of%20sexual%20and%20gender-based%20violence%20(SGBV).%20In%20turn%2C%20it%20has%20a%20compounding%20impact%20that%20worsens%20gender%20vulnerability%20in%20societies%20that%20have%20experienced%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20such%20conflict-driven%20areas%2C%20women%20are%20subjected%20to%20various%20sorts%20of%20violence%20as%20their%20bodies%20are%20viewed%20as%20%E2%80%9Cinstruments%20of%20war.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Manipur%2C%20the%20second-class%20gender%20identities%20of%20women%20disproportionately%20intersect%20with%20their%20ethnic%20identities%2C%20which%20leaves%20them%20as%20the%20gatekeepers%20of%20honour%20of%20their%20ethnic%20group%20and%20an%20accessible%20avenue%20of%20violation%20for%20the%20other%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeconstructing%20the%20act%20of%20parading%20women%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98other%E2%80%99%20ethnic%20group%20naked%20onto%20open%20fields%20by%20a%20group%20of%20bystanders%20clarifies%20that%20it%20is%20not%20an%20isolated%20incident%20of%20aggravated%20agony.%20Women%E2%80%99s%20subjugation%20is%20a%20result%20of%20the%20patriarchal%20structure%20and%20ideology%2C%20crimes%20against%20women%20are%20not%20committed%20merely%20by%20an%20individual%2C%20but%20are%20driven%20by%20the%20intersectional%20framework%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20222659%2Fimage-1151.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22952%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20222659%2Fimage-1151.png%20952w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20222659%2Fimage-1151-300x162.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664260%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22513%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EWomen%20leaders%20hold%20a%20demonstration%20against%20the%20assault%20on%20women%20in%20Manipur%2C%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20on%20July%2020%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHindutva%E2%80%99s%20paternalistic%20lens%20and%20patriarchy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20argued%20in%20length%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fbig-talk-small-action-modi-govts-work-on-womens-empowerment-in-the-last-9-years%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20campaign%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Beti%20Bachao%20Beti%20Padhao%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Save%20the%20Daughter%2C%20Educate%20the%20Daughter)%20launched%20in%202015%20was%20aimed%20at%20preventing%20gender-biased%20sex%20selective%20elimination%2C%20ensuring%20survival%20and%20protection%20of%20the%20girl%20child%2C%20and%20ensuring%20education%20and%20participation%20of%20the%20girl%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20explicitly%20states%20that%20this%20campaign%20focuses%20on%20%E2%80%9Cchallenging%20mindsets%20and%20deep-rooted%20patriarchy%20in%20the%20societal%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20year%2C%20Modi%20strongly%20endorsed%20a%20small%20grassroots%20campaign%20that%20started%20in%20Haryana%2C%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fbengali%2Fmovies%2Fphoto-features%2Fcelebs-post-selfiewithdaughter-in-support-of-narendra-modis-campaign%2Fphotostory%2F47893454.cms%5C%22%3E%23SelfieWithDaughter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20fathers%20were%20asked%20to%20tweet%20photos%20with%20their%20daughters%20and%20upload%20them%20to%20the%20Foundation%20website.%20This%20received%20widespread%20media%20coverage%20nationally%20and%20internationally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.warwick.ac.uk%2Findex.php%2Ffeministdissent%2Farticle%2Fview%2F759%5C%22%3Eargued%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Amrita%20Chhachhi%20in%20a%20recent%20paper%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20campaigns%20aimed%20to%20present%20a%20progressive%20modernity%20which%20strategically%20feeds%20into%20the%20Hindutva%20project%20of%20India%20being%20recognised%20as%20a%20global%20player%20and%20garners%20acceptability%20and%20recognition%20by%20international%20development%20organisations.%20Modi%20mentioned%20the%20campaign%20when%20he%20addressed%20the%20CEOs%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20and%20in%20Wembley%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3ETime%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EMagazine%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20this%20as%20a%20personal%20crusade%20for%20gender%20equality%20the%20prime%20minister%20had%20started%20since%20he%20came%20to%20power.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScholar%20Hussain%20(2015)%20notes%20that%20this%20functions%20as%20%E2%80%98face%20work%E2%80%99%20in%20%E2%80%98impression%20management%E2%80%99%20which%20creates%20a%20social%20image%20that%20%E2%80%98aligns%20with%20the%20Indian%E2%80%99s%20aspirational%20economic%20image%20of%20a%20neoliberal%20powerhouse.%E2%80%9D%20In%20addition%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20personalised%20alignment%20of%20Modi%20with%20these%20campaigns%20and%20other%20social%20policies%20fosters%20a%20new%20%E2%80%98paternalist%E2%80%99%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnarendra-modi-democracy-india-white-house%5C%22%3ESix%20(Of%20Many)%20Reasons%20Why%20PM%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Words%20on%20Democracy%20in%20the%20White%20House%20Ring%20Hollow%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECollateral%20damage%3A%20alienation%20and%20the%20diminishing%20agency%20of%20Manipuri%20women%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20need%20for%20a%20serious%20inquiry%20into%20the%20lack%20of%20accountability%20and%20inability%20to%20take%20action%20by%20the%20institutions%20of%20the%20country%20that%20parades%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-g20-tourism-meet-goa-festival-of-democracy-2024-general-elections-101687342488009.html%5C%22%3Eideals%20of%20%E2%80%98democracy%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20numerous%20G20%20conferences%20and%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20have%20showcased%20that%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20(NCW)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2023%2F07%2F20%2Fvideo-of-kuki-women-ncw-ignored-complaint-about-it-submitted-38-days-ago%5C%22%3Ehad%20ignored%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20complaint%20filed%20on%20June%2012%20that%20had%20described%20other%20instances%20of%20sexual%20violence.%20However%2C%20the%20NCW%20chairperson%20took%20more%20than%20a%20month%20to%20take%20suo%20motu%20cognisance%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20and%20that%20too%20only%20after%20the%20video%20went%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20is%2C%20why%20exactly%20does%20this%20country%20and%20the%20state%20machineries%20need%20a%20graphic%20depiction%20of%20violence%20against%20women%20to%20act%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20that%2C%20the%20continuous%20circulation%20of%20the%20videos%20and%20images%2C%20blurred%20or%20otherwise%20by%20outlets%20and%20people%20alike%2C%20is%20also%20a%20form%20of%20violence%20against%20the%20women%20whose%20autonomy%20and%20dignity%20were%20violated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20commendable%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-women-paraded-news-cji-dy-chandrachud-supreme-court-condemns-viral-video-says-deeply-disturbing-unacceptable-101689830929912.html%5C%22%3Ehas%20asked%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20government%20to%20act%20immediately%20but%20it%20should%20not%20be%20forgotten%20that%20the%20same%20apex%20body%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fsc-dismisses-plea-against-internet-shutdown-in-manipur-8783542%2F%5C%22%3Ehad%20declined%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20hear%20the%20urgent%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20internet%20shutdown%20as%20the%20high%20court%20was%20already%20looking%20into%20it%20earlier%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20should%20also%20be%20noted%20that%20despite%20the%20recommendations%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20collegium%2C%20the%20Manipur%20high%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eastmojo.com%2Fmanipur%2F2023%2F07%2F06%2Fsc-collegium-recommends-chief-justices-for-manipur-hc-6-others%2F%5C%22%3Ehas%20not%20seen%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20Chief%20Justice%20since%20February%206%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20two%20survivors%20of%20the%20violence%20issued%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-police-women-video-paraded-naked%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20saying%20that%20the%20Manipur%20police%20were%20present%20when%20the%20violence%20was%20being%20inflicted%20upon%20the%20women%2C%20as%20seen%20in%20the%20video%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20do%20anything%20to%20help%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20state%20that%20has%20imposed%20curfews%2C%20internet%20restrictions%2C%20and%20heavy%20militarisation%2C%20the%20violence%20has%20curiously%20not%20even%20shown%20signs%20of%20declining%2C%20and%20it%20is%20time%20to%20discard%20the%20apathy%20and%20complicity%20and%20acknowledge%20the%20perpetual%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20a%20series%20of%20field-based%20reports%2C%20spotlighting%20lesser-known%20cross-cutting%20humanitarian%20issues%20that%20are%20emanating%20from%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20in%20Manipur.%20In%20addition%20to%20understanding%20the%20socio-economic%20impact%20of%20the%20conflict%2C%20the%20series%20also%20seeks%20to%20map%20out%20instances%20of%20resilience%2C%20local%20innovations%20in%20humanitarian%20action%2C%20and%20examples%20of%20community%20peace-building%20in%20the%20context.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Mapping%20Humanitarianism%20Initiative%20(MHI)%20is%20being%20undertaken%20by%20the%20CNES%20in%20close%20collaboration%20with%20Peace%20Centre%20Nagaland%2C%20located%20in%20Ch%C3%BCmoukedima.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETavleen%20Kaur%20is%20Senior%20Research%20Assistant%20with%20CNES%20and%20Team-Lead%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fswabhimaannetin.wordpress.com%2F%5C%22%3ESwabhimaan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Archisha%20Tiwari%20and%20Anvitha%20Gowda%20are%20Research%20Analysts%20with%20CNES%20and%20members%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fswabhimaannetin.wordpress.com%2F%5C%22%3ESwabhi