nAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fgod-is-a-woman-doc-panama-venice-critics-week-1235678144%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fgod-is-a-woman-doc-panama-venice-critics-week-1235678144%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Would%20Have%20Put%20Him%20In%20Jail...%5C%22%3A%20AAP%20After%20Its%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Is%20Suspended%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAAP%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20has%20been%20suspended%20from%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20monsoon%20session%20amid%20a%20face-off%20in%20Parliament%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20opposition%20over%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%20Mr%20Singh%20was%20suspended%20for%20allegedly%20jumping%20into%20the%20well%20of%20the%20House%20and%20raising%20slogans%2C%20and%20refusing%20to%20go%20back%20despite%20being%20warned%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Chairman.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspension%2C%20which%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20have%20locked%20horns%20over%20the%20Centre's%20ordinance%20on%20control%20of%20bureaucrats%20in%20Delhi%2C%20invited%20a%20sharp%20reaction%20from%20the%20AAP.%C2%A0%20The%20party%20said%20Mr%20Singh%20is%20a%20strong%20voice%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20the%20BJP%20would%20have%20put%20him%20in%20jail%20if%20it%20had%20its%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Singh%20raises%20slogans%20and%20the%20entire%20opposition%20unites.%20It%20is%20obvious%20that%20he%20is%20a%20thorn%20in%20the%20government's%20side%20and%20they%20will%20try%20their%20best%20to%20silence%20his%20voice.%20But%20no%20matter%20what%20they%20do%2C%20be%20it%20such%20gimmicks%20or%20the%20misuse%20of%20probe%20agencies%20like%20the%20CBI%20and%20ED%2C%20the%20return%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%20is%20difficult.%20The%20legal%20wing%20will%20see%20what%20can%20be%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20AAP%20leader%20and%20Delhi%20Minister%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFloor%20leaders%20of%20opposition%20parties%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20also%20walked%20out%20of%20a%20meeting%20called%20by%20Chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20at%201%20pm%20to%20discuss%20Mr%20Singh's%20suspension.%20They%20walked%20out%20after%20the%20Chairman%20objected%20to%20Raghav%20Chadha%20of%20the%20AAP%20and%20Santanu%20Sen%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20attending%20the%20meeting%20as%20they%20are%20not%20the%20floor%20leaders%20of%20their%20respective%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20when%20Rajya%20Sabha%20proceedings%20resumed%20at%20noon%20after%20being%20adjourned%20for%20an%20hour%2C%20the%20Chairman%20allowed%20the%20question%20hour%20to%20start.%20Many%20opposition%20MPs%20pointed%20out%20that%20they%20had%20submitted%20notices%20under%20Rule%20267%2C%20seeking%20a%20long%20discussion%20on%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%20They%20also%20demanded%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20come%20to%20the%20House%20to%20make%20a%20statement%20and%20initiate%20the%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhankhar%20allowed%20the%20question%20hour%20to%20continue.%20When%20Jal%20Shakti%20Minister%20Gajendra%20Shekhawat%20was%20answering%20questions%20related%20to%20his%20ministry%2C%20AAP%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20allegedly%20jumped%20into%20the%20well%20of%20the%20House%20and%20began%20raising%20slogans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20was%20protesting%20against%20the%20question%20hour%20being%20allowed%20to%20go%20on%20when%20the%20opposition%20MPs%20were%20demanding%20a%20discussion%20under%20Rule%20267.%20He%20was%20warned%20by%20the%20Chairman%20to%20go%20back%2C%20but%20he%20did%20not%20heed%20the%20warning%20and%20kept%20raising%20slogans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Leader%20of%20the%20House%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Piyush%20Goyal%2C%20got%20up%20to%20say%20that%20this%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20discipline%20and%20code%20of%20conduct%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20and%20urged%20the%20Chairman%20to%20take%20strong%20action%20against%20Mr%20Singh.%20He%20moved%20a%20motion%20to%20suspend%20him%2C%20which%20was%20adopted%20by%20the%20House%20by%20voice%20vote.%20The%20Chairman%20then%20announced%20Mr%20Singh's%20suspension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajya%20Sabha%20has%20been%20adjourned%20till%203%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20houses%20of%20the%20Parliament%20have%20been%20disrupted%20since%20the%20monsoon%20session%20began%20on%20July%2020.%20The%20opposition%20parties%20have%20been%20demanding%20a%20detailed%20discussion%20on%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20and%20a%20statement%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20the%20issue%20inside%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Opposition%20has%20demanded%20that%20all%20other%20business%20be%20suspended%20for%20the%20day%20to%20take%20up%20the%20Manipur%20issue%2C%20the%20government%20has%20agreed%20only%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bshort-duration%20discussion%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690189920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fti2ukeug_sanjay-singh-rajya-sabha-650_625x300_24_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faap-mp-sanjay-singh-suspended-from-parliaments-monsoon-session-over-manipur-protest-4235643%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AAP%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20has%20been%20suspended%20from%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20monsoon%20session%20amid%20a%20face-off%20in%20Parliament%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20opposition%20over%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faap-mp-sanjay-singh-suspended-from-parliaments-monsoon-session-over-manipur-protest-4235643%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faap-mp-sanjay-s