ghest%20number%20of%20posts%20containing%20fake%20news%20were%20reported%20during%20the%20second%20Covid-19%20wave%20and%20the%20fact%20checking%20body%20took%20action%20against%20more%20than%205%2C000%20posts%20in%20April%202021%20and%20nearly%20800%20posts%20in%20May%20that%20year%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThakur%2C%20while%20responding%20to%20a%20different%20unstarred%20question%20from%20TMC%20leader%20Derek%20O%E2%80%99Brien%2C%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20blocked%20public%20access%20to%20635%20URLs%2C%20including%2010%20websites%20and%20five%20applications%2C%20since%20December%202021%20under%20the%20IT%20Rules%2C%202021.%20It%20did%20not%20provide%20details%20of%20these%20URLs%2C%20%3Cem%3ENewslaundry%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fout-of-nearly-1-2-lakh-queries-in-3-years-pibs-fact-check-unit-acted-on-1223%5C%22%3EOut%20of%20Nearly%201.2%20Lakh%20Queries%20in%203%20Years%2C%20PIB%E2%80%99s%20Fact-Check%20Unit%20Acted%20on%201%2C223%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20statement%20said%20the%20PIB%20undertakes%20a%20%E2%80%9Crigorous%20process%E2%80%9D%20of%20fact-checking%20involving%20%E2%80%9Cmultiple%20layers%20of%20cross-checking%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ENewslaundry%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20PIB%20had%20revealed%20that%20of%20the%201.2%20lakh%20requests%20it%20had%20received%20for%20fact%20checking%20information%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20it%20had%20only%20acted%20upon%201%2C223%20of%20them%20%E2%80%93%20a%20modest%201%25%20action%20rate%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PIB%20in%20its%20response%20also%20admitted%20that%20this%20fact-check%20unit%20is%20currently%20operating%20without%20any%20statutory%20basis%20or%20institutional%20mechanisms%20and%20the%20new%20fact-check%20units%20to%20be%20set%20up%20under%20the%20notified%20IT%20Amendment%20Rules%2C%202023%2C%20have%20not%20been%20established%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fpib-fact-check-unit-claims-our-article-on-its-work-is-misleading-five-reasons-why-it-is-wrong%5C%22%3EPIB%20Fact-Check%20Unit%20Claims%20Our%20Article%20on%20Its%20Work%20Is%20%E2%80%98Misleading%E2%80%99.%20Five%20Reasons%20Why%20It%20Is%20Wrong.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bombay%20high%20court%20had%20called%20these%20amendments%20%E2%80%9Cexcessive%E2%80%9D%20while%20hearing%20pleas%20challenging%20the%20new%20rules.%20The%20amendments%20empower%20the%20government%20to%20take%20action%20against%20%E2%80%9Cfake%20news%E2%80%9D%20about%20it%20on%20social%20media%20through%20a%20fact%20check%20unit.%20The%20court%20had%20asked%20who%20will%20fact-check%20the%20fact%20checking%20units%2C%20adding%20that%20one%20cannot%20%E2%80%9Cbring%20a%20hammer%20to%20kill%20an%20ant.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20amended%20IT%20Rules%20have%20been%20under%20fire%20from%20several%20quarters%20for%20curbing%20free%20speech%20and%20amounting%20to%20censorship.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690189845000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F21180429%2FScreenshot-291.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbjp-government-blocked-access-to-635-urls-10-websites-under-it-rules-2021-anurag-thakur%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thakur%20also%20said%20that%20the%20PIB's%20fact%20checking%20unit%20had%20taken%20action%20against%20more%20than%2028%2C000%20posts%20containing%20fake%20news.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbjp-government-blocked-access-to-635-urls-10-websites-under-it-rules-2021-anurag-thakur%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%