%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Economic%20Times%20reported%20the%20government's%20rejection%20of%20BYD's%20investment%20plan%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20was%20probing%20SAIC%20Motor%20Corp.'s%20local%20unit%20MG%20Motor%20India%20Pvt%20over%20alleged%20financial%20irregularities%2C%20Bloomberg%20News%20reported%20last%20year.%20MG%20Motor%20has%20since%20announced%20plans%20to%20dilute%20its%20100%25%20share%20of%20the%20business%2C%20and%20aims%20to%20have%20it%20majority-owned%20by%20an%20Indian%20firm%20in%20two%20to%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20rejection%20deals%20a%20blow%20to%20BYD's%20ambitious%20plans%20for%20India.%20The%20company%2C%20which%20entered%20the%20country%20in%202007%2C%20sought%20to%20capture%2040%25%20of%20the%20domestic%20EV%20market%20by%202030%2C%20Sanjay%20Gopalakrishnan%2C%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20its%20local%20operations%2C%20told%20Bloomberg%20in%20January.%20It's%20aiming%20to%20sell%2015%2C000%20electric%20vehicles%20in%20India%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestment%20from%20elsewhere%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20be%20at%20risk.%20After%20meeting%20with%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20the%20US%20last%20month%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20said%20Tesla%20Inc.%20is%20likely%20to%20make%20a%20significant%20investment%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690187040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fq3722mug_electric-vehicles-bloomberg_625x300_18_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-rejects-1-billion-bid-by-chinese-carmaker-to-set-up-ev-factory-report-4235853%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20rejected%20Chinese%20carmaker%20BYD%20Co.'s%20proposal%20to%20build%20a%20%241%20billion%20electric-vehicle%2