3Epic.twitter.com%2FaMVOt0JRbM%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20MP%2FCG%2FRajasthan%20(%40ANI_MP_CG_RJ)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI_MP_CG_RJ%2Fstatus%2F1683375294286299136%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2024%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gudha%20reached%20near%20Speaker%20CP%20Joshi's%20chair%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bred%20diary%26quot%3B%20and%20had%20an%20argument%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20diary%20was%20allegedly%20recovered%20by%20Mr%20Gudha%20in%20the%20past%20during%20an%20IT%20raid%20on%20Ashok%20Gehlot's%20associate%2C%20Dharmendra%20Singh%20Rathore.%20The%20sacked%20former%20minister%20says%20it%20could%20%26quot%3Bexpose%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gehlot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Mr%20Gudha%20waved%20the%20red-coloured%20diary%2C%20the%20speaker%20asked%20him%20to%20come%20to%20his%20chamber.%20After%20some%20time%2C%20the%20sacked%20minister%20reached%20near%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Shanti%20Dhariwal%20and%20confronted%20him%20while%20he%20stood%20to%20speak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MLAs%20created%20an%20uproar%20and%20rushed%20to%20the%20well%20of%20the%20House%20over%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bred%20diary%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20speaker%20then%20adjourned%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20House%20began%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20Mr%20Gudha%20told%20reporters%20that%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bdisclose%26quot%3B%20details%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bred%20diary%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20diary%20contained%20some%20%26quot%3Bsecrets%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajendra%20Singh%20Gudha%20was%20sacked%20last%20week%2C%20hours%20after%20raising%20questions%20in%20the%20Assembly%20on%20his%20own%20government's%20success%20in%20controlling%20crimes%20against%20women.%C2%A0Reacting%20to%20Mr%20Gudha's%20sacking%20from%20the%20state%20cabinet%2C%20Rajasthan%20Congress%20chief%20Govind%20Singh%20Dotasra%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-ministers-call-rajasthan-congress-chief-on-minister-rajendra-singh-gudhas-sacking-4232373%5C%22%3Eon%20Saturday%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BInclusion%20of%20a%20minister%20or%20their%20dismissal%20is%20up%20to%20a%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20he%20acted%20accordingly.%20It%20is%20the%20right%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20true%20and%20should%20be%20accepted%20that%20we%20have%20failed%20to%20ensure%20women's%20safety.%20Instead%20of%20Manipur%2C%20we%20should%20look%20within%20ourselves%20-%20why%20atrocities%20on%20women%20have%20increased%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gudha%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dotasra%20also%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20trying%20to%20divert%20attention%20from%20the%20viral%20video%20of%20Manipur%20horror%20by%20picking%20one%20or%20two%20incidents%20from%20the%20Congress-ruled%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajendra%20Singh%20Gudha%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgot-punished-for-rajasthan-minister-after-being-sacked-from-cabinet-4230920%5C%22%3Ehas%20said%20that%20he%20was%20punished%20for%20speaking%20the%20truth%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20speak%20the%20truth.%20That%20is%20who%20I%20am.%20I%20follow%20my%20conscience.%20I%20got%20punished%20for%20speaking%20the%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sisters%20and%20daughters%20of%20the%20Udaipurwati%20Assembly%20constituency%2C%20who%20have%20helped%20me%20win%20the%20elections%2C%20trusted%20me%20so%20that%20I%20could%20respect%20and%20protect%20them.%20But%20the%20way%20in%20which%20newspapers%20today%20are%20flooded%20with%20incidents%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20against%20our%20sisters%20and%20mothers%20shows%20that%20Rajasthan%20is%20number%20one%20in%20atrocities%20against%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccused%20of%20cri