-1-2-billion-loan-report-123072400158_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20the%20loan%20terms%20are%20reworked%20successfully%2C%20the%20creditors%20are%20expected%20to%20drop%20their%20demand%20for%20accelerated%20repayment%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbyju-s-reaches-agreement-to-rework-terms-of-1-2-billion-loan-report-123072400158_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Remembering%20Tilak%2C%20the%20Father%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Revolution%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F31235419%2Fbal-gangadhar-tilak.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAmongst%20the%20stalwarts%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle%20in%20the%20pre-Gandhi%20era%2C%20the%20name%20of%20Lokmanya%20Tilak%20stands%20out%20as%20a%20colossus%20for%20his%20supreme%20courage%2C%20sacrifice%2C%20selflessness%20and%20for%20his%20historic%20role%20in%20the%20early%20phase%20of%20the%20independence%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBal%20Gangadhar%20Tilak%20was%20born%20on%20July%2023%2C%201856%2C%20at%20Ratnagiri%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20in%20a%20middle-class%20family.%20Soon%20after%20his%20graduation%2C%20Tilak%20developed%20a%20serious%20concern%20for%20the%20social%20and%20political%20problems%20of%20his%20day.%20He%20wanted%20to%20reform%20the%20system%20of%20education%20introduced%20by%20the%20British%20and%20started%20a%20society%20to%20spread%20education%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20restless%20mind%20could%20not%20remain%20limited%20to%20one%20field.%20He%20soon%20ventured%20into%20journalism%20and%20started%20a%20Marathi%20paper%2C%20%3Cem%3EKesari%3C%2Fem%3E.%20He%20passionately%20wrote%20on%20reforming%20Indian%20society.%20On%20the%20problem%20of%20untouchability%20he%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20not%20recognise%20even%20God%20if%20he%20said%20that%20untouchability%20was%20ordained%20by%20him.%E2%80%9D%20While%20advocating%20social%20reforms%2C%20he%20turned%20the%20attention%20of%20people%20to%20the%20political%20problem%20%E2%80%94%20liberation%20of%20India%20from%20British%20rule.%20He%20began%20writing%20articles%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EKesari%3C%2Fem%3E%20asserting%20every%20Indian%E2%80%99s%20birthright%20to%20be%20free.%20This%20was%20a%20revolutionary%20doctrine%20to%20be%20preached%20in%20those%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20brought%20him%20into%20conflict%20with%20the%20empire%20and%20he%20was%20convicted%20on%20the%20charge%20of%20sedition%20in%201897.%20However%2C%20this%20conviction%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20blessing%20in%20disguise%3A%20from%20a%20provincial%20leader%2C%20Tilak%20became%20a%20national%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201889%20(the%20year%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20was%20born)%2C%20Tilak%20attended%20the%20Bombay%20session%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20presided%20by%20Sir%20William%20Wedderburn.%20Tilak%20was%20then%2033.%20Two%20other%20young%20Congressmen%2C%20who%20were%20to%20become%20his%20contemporaries%2C%20also%20appeared%20on%20the%20Congress%20platform%20for%20the%20first%20time%20%E2%80%94%20Lala%20Lajpat%20Rai%20(34)%20and%20Gopal%20Krishna%20Gokhale%20(33).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20since%20its%20birth%20in%201885%2C%20was%20dominated%20by%20the%20Moderates%20who%20had%20faith%20in%20British%20sense%20of%20justice%20and%20fair%20play%2C%20and%20believed%20in%20constitutional%20and%20lawful%20methods%20of%20agitation.%20This%2C%20however%2C%20dramatically%20changed%20with%20Lord%20Curzon%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20partition%20the%20sate%20of%20Bengal.%20The%20youth%20of%20India%20moved%20towards%20militant%20politics%20and%20direct%20action.%20Along%20with%20Bipin%20Chandra%20Pal%20and%20Lala%20Lajpat%20Rai%2C%20Tilak%20seized%20the%20opportunity%20of%20disillusionment%20against%20the%20British%20and%20denounced%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20mendicancy%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Moderates.%20The%20trio%20of%20Bal-Pal-Lal%2C%20along%20with%20Aurobindo%20Ghose%2C%20became%20popular%20as%20%E2%80%9Cextremists%E2%80%9D%2C%20though%20they%20preferred%20to%20call%20themselves%20%E2%80%9Cnationalists%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20recalls%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Discovery%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20coming%20of%20age%20of%20the%20National%20Congress%2C%20which%20had%20been%20founded%20in%201885%2C%20a%20new%20type%20of%20leadership%20appeared%2C%20more%20aggressive%20and%20defiant%20and%20representing%20the%20much%20larger%20numbers%20of%20the%20lower%20middle%20classes%20as%20well%20as%20students%20and%20young%20men.%20The%20powerful%20agitation%20against%20the%20partition%20of%20Bengal%20had%20thrown%20up%20many%20able%20and%20aggressive%20leaders%20there%20of%20this%20type%2C%20but%20the%20real%20symbol%20of%20the%20new%20age%20was%20Bal%20Gangadhar%20Tilak%20from%20Maharashtra.%20The%20old%20leadership%20was%20represented%20also%20by%20a%20Maratha%2C%20a%20very%20able%20and%20a%20young%20man%2C%20Gopal%20Krishna%20Gokhale.%20Revolutionary%20slogans%20were%20in%20the%20air%2C%20tempers%20ran%20high%20and%20conflict%20was%20inevitable.%20To%20avoid%20this%2C%20the%20old%20patriarch%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20Dadabhai%20Naoroji%2C%20universally%20respected%20and%20regarded%20as%20the%20father%20of%20the%20country%2C%20was%20brought%20out%20of%20his%20retirement.%20The%20respite%20was%20brief%20and%20in%201907%20the%20clash%20came%2C%20resulting%20apparently%20in%20a%20victory%20for%20the%20old%20moderate%20section.%20(But)%20there%20was%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20politically-%20minded%20people%20in%20India%20favoured%20Tilak%20and%20his%20group.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2024%2C%201903%2C%20an%20arrest%20warrant%20was%20served%20on%20Tilak%20in%20Bombay.%20The%20historic%20trial%20of%20Tilak%20on%20charges%20of%20sedition%20began%20on%20July%2013.%20He%20was%20convicted%20and%20deported%20to%20Mandalay%2C%20Burma%2C%20where%20he%20was%20to%20spend%20the%20next%2011%20years%20of%20his%20life.%20On%20hearing%20the%20verdict%2C%20Tilak%20defiantly%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CAll%20I%20wish%20to%20say%20is%20that%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20verdict%20of%20the%20jury%2C%20I%20maintain%20that%20I%20am%20innocent.%20There%20are%20higher%20powers%20that%20rule%20the%20destiny%20of%20things%20and%20it%20may%20be%20the%20will%20of%20providence%20that%20the%20cause%20which%20I%20represent%20may%20prosper%20more%20by%20my%20suffering%20than%20by%20my%20remaining%20free.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Mandalay%2C%20Tilak%20soon%20settled%20himself%20into%20the%20routine%20of%20writing%20and%20thinking.%20The%20man%20of%20action%20absorbed%20himself%20in%20reading%2C%20in%20learning%20new%20things%20and%20in%20contemplating%20on%20the%20true%20message%20of%20the%20Gita.%20A%20most%20fruitful%20result%20of%20this%20constant%20reading%20and%20reflection%20was%20the%20Geeta%20Rahasya.%20On%20June%208%2C%201914%2C%20Tilak%20was%20informed%20that%20his%20exile%20was%20over.%20He%20was%20then%2058%2C%20and%20his%20health%20was%20broken%2C%20but%20his%20spirit%20was%20unbowed.%20On%20his%20return%20to%20India%2C%20he%20resumed%20his%20political%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Tilak%E2%80%99s%20biographer%2C%20D.V.%20Tamhankar%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20year%201916%20was%20the%20most%20eventful%20in%20Tilak%E2%80%99s%20career.%20The%20early%20part%20of%20the%20year%20saw%20the%20foundation%20of%20the%20Home%20Rule%20League%2C%20its%20phenomenal%20success%2C%20the%20presentation%20of%20the%20public%20purse%20on%20Tilak%E2%80%99s%2061st%20birthday%2C%20and%20his%20legal%20victory%20in%20the%20last%20sedition%20of%20the%20Lucknow%20Congress%2C%20which%20marks%20the%20zenith%20not%20only%20of%20Tilak%E2%80%99s%20life%2C%20but%20also%2C%20perhaps%2C%20of%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Congress.%20Tilak%2C%20who%20had%20previously%20borne%20a%20reputation%20for%20intransigence%20in%20politics%2C%20now%20appears%20in%20the%20role%20of%20a%20constructive%20and%20conciliatory%20stateman.%20The%20days%20of%20fiery%20speeches%20and%20denunciations%20are%20over%3B%20a%20new%20phase%20of%20compromise%20and%20responsive%20cooperation%20begins.%20He%20is%20seen%20at%20his%20best%20at%20the%20Lucknow%20Congress%20which%20marks%20a%20definite%20stage%20in%20the%20political%20evolution%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%20Under%20Tilak%E2%80%99s%20inspiration%2C%20there%20was%20a%20united%20demand%20for%20Swaraj%2C%20the%20first%20occasion%20when%20Muslims%20and%20Hindus%2C%20Moderates%20and%20extremists%2C%20Parsees%20and%20others%20spoke%20together%20with%20one%20voice%20to%20demand%20vital%20reforms.%20Tilak%20emerged%20as%20a%20messiah%20of%20Hindu-Muslim%20unity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20formation%20of%20the%20Indian%20Home%20Rule%20League%20was%20the%20crowning%20achievement%20of%20Tilak%E2%80%99s%20political%20career.%20He%20had%20worked%20for%2035%20years%20to%20give%20concrete%20shape%20to%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20political%20aspirations%2C%20largely%20aroused%20and%20sustained%20to%20by%20his%20own%20exertions%20and%20sufferings%2C%20and%20his%20labours%20at%20last%20bore%20fruit.%20The%20country%20could%20now%20speak%20out%20and%20demand%20its%20birthright%20without%20fear.%20The%20people%20had%20become%20conscious%20of%20their%20rights%3B%20their%20aspirations%20had%20assumed%20a%20definite%20shape%2C%20and%20they%20realised%20that%20a%20foreign%20bureaucracy%20%E2%80%9Ccannot%20be%20mended%20but%20must%20be%20ended%E2%80%9D.%20Now%20the%20time%20had%20surely%20come%2C%20Tilak%20said%2C%20to%20demand%20control%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20affairs.%20But%20if%20the%20demand%20for%20Swaraj%20was%20to%20be%20effective%2C%20it%20must%20be%20made%20through%20a%20powerful%20and%20organised%20body.%20The%20Home%20Rule%20League%20was%20to%20be%20that%20body.%20It%20was%20founded%20on%20April%2028%2C%201916%2C%20with%20its%20headquarters%20in%20Pune.%20A%20similar%20Home%20Rule%20League%20was%20started%20by%20Annie%20Besant%20(who%20the%20following%20year%20became%20the%20first%20woman%20president%20of%20INC)%20with%20its%20headquarters%20in%20Madras.%20Both%20the%20Home%20Rule%20Leagues%20supplemented%20each%20other.%20The%20Home%20Rule%20Movement%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20new%20phase%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20for%20freedom.%20It%20placed%20before%20the%20country%20a%20concrete%20scheme%20of%20self-government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%2C%20while%20unveiling%20a%20portrait%20of%20Lokmanya%20Tilak%20in%20Parliament%20on%20July%2028%2C%201956%2C%20concluded%20his%20glowing%20tribute%20to%20Tilak%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20not%20my%20privilege%20to%20come%20into%20close%20contact%20with%20Tilak.%20When%20he%20was%20at%20the%20height%20of%20his%20career%2C%20I%20was%20away%20in%20a%20far%20country%2C%20still%20a%20student.%20But%20even%20there%20his%20voice%20and%20his%20story%20reached%20us%20and%20fired%20our%20imagination.%20We%20early%20grew%20up%20under%20that%20influence%20and%20were%20moulded%20by%20it.%20In%20a%20sense%2C%20India%20to%20the%20youth%20of%20that%20time%20was%20what%20had%20been%20presented%20by%20Tilak%2C%20through%20what%20he%20said%20and%20what%20he%20wrote%2C%20and%20above%20all%2C%20what%20he%20suffered.%20That%20was%20the%20inheritance%20that%20Gandhiji%20had%20to%20start%20his%20vast%20movements%20with.%20If%20there%20had%20not%20been%20that%20moulding%20of%20the%20Indian%20people%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20imagination%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20youth%20by%20Lokmanya%2C%20it%20would%20not%20have%20been%20easy%20for%20the%20next%20step%20to%20be%20taken.%20Thus%2C%20in%20this%20historical%20panorama%2C%20we%20can%20see%20one%20great%20man%20after%20another%20coming%20and%20performing%20acts%20of%20destiny%20and%20history%20which%20have%20cumulatively%20led%20to%20the%20achievement%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20freedom.%20We%20meet%20here%20not%20only%20to%20unveil%20the%20picture%20of%20this%20great%20man%2C%20the%20Father%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Revolution%2C%20but%20to%20remember%20him%20and%20to%20be%20inspired%20by%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETilak%20was%20the%20tallest%20of%20the%20leaders%20of%20his%20generation%20who%20prepared%20the%20nation%20for%20the%20trials%20and%20triumphs%20of%20the%20Gandhian%20era.%20On%20August%201%2C%201920%2C%20a%20day%20before%20Gandhiji%20launched%20the%20Non-Cooperation%20Movement%2C%20Tilak%20passed%20away%2C%20thus%20marking%20the%20end%20of%20one%20and%20beginning%20of%20another%20era%20that%20culminated%20in%20the%20realisation%20of%20his%20dream%20of%20free%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPraveen%20Davar%20is%20a%20columnist%20and%20the%20author%20of%3C%2Fem%3E%20Freedom%20Struggle%20and%20Beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690174709000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F31235419%2Fbal-gangadhar-tilak.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fremembering-tilak-the-father-of-indias-revolution%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tilak%20was%20the%20tallest%20of%20the%20leaders%20of%20his%20generation%20who%20prepared%20the%20nation%20for%20the%20trials%20and%20triumphs%20of%20the%20Gandhian%20era.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fremembering-tilak-the-father-of-indias-revolution%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stock%20Market%20Live%3A%20Sensex%2C%20Nifty50%20trade%20flat%3B%20RIL%20down%201%25%20post%20weak%20Q1%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690174220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Fmisc%2F2023-03%2F21%2Ffull%2Fmarket-stocks-stock-market-trading-stock-market-1679390216-0792620.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-july-