gless%20platitudes%20and%20whataboutery.%20Not%20only%20are%20they%20guilty%20of%20inaction%2C%20but%20also%20of%20brushing%20the%20horror%20under%20the%20carpet.%20In%20that%2C%20they%20are%20complicit.%20They%20too%20are%20guilty%2C%20but%20who%20will%20hold%20them%20to%20account%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGovernment%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20impossible%20to%20believe%20that%20nobody%20in%20authority%20in%20the%20State%20of%20Manipur%20knew%20of%20the%20horror%20until%20the%20video%20surfaced%20last%20week.%20Consider%20this%3A%20An%20armed%20mob%2C%20about%20a%20thousand%20strong%2C%20burns%20houses%20and%20hutments%20in%20village%20after%20village%20barely%2030%20km%20from%20the%20capital%20city%20of%20Imphal.%20That%E2%80%99s%20less%20than%20the%20distance%20from%20one%20end%20of%20Delhi%20to%20the%20other.%20The%20area%20where%20the%20women%20were%20paraded%20and%20ravaged%20was%20barely%20three%20km%20from%20a%20check-post.%20That%E2%80%99s%20less%20than%20the%20distance%20from%20one%20end%20of%20the%20Central%20Vista%20to%20the%20other.%20Are%20we%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20people%20in%20authority%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20was%20happening%3F%20What%20did%20they%20do%20apart%20from%20remaining%20silent%20and%20failing%20to%20react%3F%20Emulate%20Nero%3F%20Intelligence%20failure%20or%20stupidity%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20now%20come%20to%20be%20known%20that%20the%20women%20and%20men%20were%20with%20the%20police%20when%20the%20savages%20took%20them%20away.%20They%20were%20about%20two%20km%20away%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fmanipur-viral-video-incident-naked-women-india-best-police-station-geolocation-2409953-2023-07-21%5C%22%3Ebest%20police%20station%20in%20India%202020%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Are%20we%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20police%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20was%20happening%3F%20If%20they%20knew%20what%20was%20happening%2C%20what%20did%20they%20do%3F%20Did%20they%20inform%20%E2%80%98higher-ups%E2%80%99%3F%20If%20yes%2C%20what%20did%20the%20%E2%80%98higher-ups%E2%80%99%20do%3F%20If%20not%2C%20why%20not%3F%20Are%20the%20police%20equally%20guilty%2C%20if%20not%20complicit%3F%20We%20will%20never%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConspiracy%20of%20silence%20%E2%80%93%20Part%201%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVery%20conveniently%2C%20internet%20was%20shut%20down%20under%20government%20orders.%20If%20nothing%20untoward%20was%20happening%2C%20what%20was%20the%20need%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20internet%3F%20It%20is%20obvious%20that%20the%20government%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20horror%20and%20wanted%20to%20set%20up%20an%20iron%20curtain.%20Had%20the%20events%20of%20the%20day%20been%20made%20known%2C%20and%20the%20illegal%20shutdown%20not%20taken%20place%2C%20the%20video%20would%20have%20possibly%20surfaced%20the%20same%20day%20and%20compelled%20an%20indulgent%20government%20to%20act.%20Consider%20the%20larger%20implication%20of%20this%20conspiracy%20of%20silence%3A%20a%20civil%20war-like%20situation%20was%20generated%20and%20prevailed%20for%20several%20weeks%20in%20Manipur%20leaving%20about%20150%20dead%2C%20more%20than%20300%20injured%20and%20wounded%2C%20and%20more%20than%2050%2C000%20rendered%20homeless.%20Not%20a%20word%20of%20condemnation%2C%20not%20a%20word%20of%20anguish%20and%20pain.%20Speech%20is%20silver%2C%20but%20silence%20is%20golden%2C%20I%20suppose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%2C%20the%20whole%20world%20knows%20about%20the%20parading%20of%20naked%20women%2C%20the%20gang%20rape%20and%20the%20murders%2C%20something%20that%20the%20government%20in%20Imphal%20just%20about%2030%20km%20away%20was%20blissfully%20unaware%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conspiracy%20of%20silence%20continues%20with%20an%20attempt%20to%20shoot%20the%20messenger.%20Twitter%20has%20been%20told%20to%20take%20down%20the%20offending%20video%20(how%20did%20it%20surface%3F)%20and%20we%20know%20what%20will%20happen%20if%20they%20don%E2%80%99t.%20Barkha%20Dutt%2C%20an%20award-winning%20journalist%20has%20been%20also%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBDUTT%2Fstatus%2F1681977760984743936%5C%22%3Eserved%20with%20some%20objectionable%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20concerned%20authorities.%20Hush.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Manipur%20Video%3A%20What%20Connects%203%20Kuki%20Women%20Stripped%2C%20Paraded%20Naked%20to%20Manorama%20and%20Bilkis%20Bano%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fmanipur-video-kuki-women-stripped-manorama-bilkis-bano%5C%22%3EManipur%20Video%3A%20What%20Connects%203%20Kuki%20Women%20Stripped%2C%20Paraded%20Naked%20to%20Manorama%20and%20Bilkis%20Bano%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeafening%20silence%20%E2%80%93%20Part%202%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20two%20weeks%20after%20the%20horror%2C%20somebody%20mustered%20the%20courage%20to%20officially%20report%20the%20incident%20to%20the%20police%20in%20Kangkokpi%20district%20on%20May%2018.%20The%20police%20took%20the%20complaint%20on%20record%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20it%20%E2%80%93%20nothing%20else.%20Ho-hum%2C%20these%20things%20happen%20in%20a%20civil%20war-like%20situation%2C%20so%20what%E2%80%99s%20new%3F%20Well%2C%20if%20there%20is%20a%20civil%20war-like%20situation%20in%20the%20state%2C%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20the%20home%20minister%20of%20the%20state%20do%20something%20about%20it%3F%20Or%20is%20it%20for%20the%20chief%20minister%20to%20act%3F%20What%20if%20the%20home%20minister%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%20are%20one%20and%20the%20same%2C%20as%20in%20this%20case%3F%20Who%20should%20take%20the%20blame%3F%20Well%2C%20somebody%20has%20to%20take%20the%20blame%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%2C%20and%20the%20buck%20must%20stop%20somewhere%2C%20but%20where%3F%20Maybe%20it%20should%20stop%20with%20the%20person%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmanipur-cm-biren-singh-reverses-decision-to-resign-under-public-pressure%5C%22%3Etore%20up%20the%20resignation%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Pretty%20nasty%20thing%20to%20do.%20Somebody%20wants%20to%20resign%2C%20or%20so%20it%20seems%2C%20and%20he%20is%20prevented%20from%20doing%20so.%20Where%20is%20freedom%20of%20action%3F%20How%20can%20anyone%20compel%20somebody%20to%20remain%20a%20chief%20minister%20if%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%3F%20Anyone%20can%20be%20a%20deputy%20chief%20minister%2C%20but%20chief%20minister%3F%20Heavens!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20complaint%20cum%20zero%20FIR%20registered%20on%20May%2018%20reached%20the%20jurisdictional%20police%20station%20in%20Thoubal%20district%20after%20more%20than%20a%20month%20on%20June%2021.%20It%20is%20registered%20and%20thank%20god%20for%20small%20mercies.%20Do%20you%20remember%20champion%20wrestlers%20had%20to%20knock%20on%20the%20doors%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20have%20their%20complaints%20registered%20as%20FIRs%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20does%20not%20say%20that%20after%20an%20FIR%20is%20registered%2C%20the%20police%20is%20duty%20bound%20to%20investigate%20the%20report%2C%20let%20alone%20investigate%20dispassionately%20and%20impartially.%20So%2C%20the%20FIR%20having%20been%20registered%2C%20the%20police%20was%20not%20legally%20obliged%20to%20investigate%20and%2C%20if%20it%20was%2C%20it%20was%20entirely%20at%20its%20own%20pace.%20Consequently%2C%20nobody%20in%20the%20police%20station%20in%20Thoubal%20district%20thought%20it%20necessary%20to%20investigate%20and%20the%20FIR%20remained%20dormant%20until%20a%20video%20of%20the%20horror%20surfaced%2C%20almost%20a%20month%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20now%2C%20Tarzan-like%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsixth-person-arrested-in-manipur-video-case-is-a-juvenile-report%5C%22%3Eswung%20into%20action%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20arrested%20a%20handful%20of%20savages.%20Perhaps%2C%20having%20no%20faith%20in%20the%20police%2C%20other%20women%20have%20taken%20the%20law%20into%20their%20own%20hands%20and%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-video-meitei-womens-group-sets-accused-mans-house-on-fire%5C%22%3Eburnt%20down%20the%20house%20of%20the%20prime%20accused%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20probably%20got%20this%20idea%20from%20the%20bulldozer%20justice%20that%20is%20being%20dispensed%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20except%20that%20the%20women%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20bulldozer%20with%20them.%20Maybe%20they%20will%20get%20arrested%20for%20arson%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20national%20security%20or%20after%20being%20branded%20as%20terrorists.%20Anything%20is%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20next%3F%20Fact%20finding%20is%20impossible.%20The%20truth%20will%20never%20come%20out.%20Deeksha%20Dwivedi%2C%20a%20practising%20lawyer%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%2C%20wanted%20to%20ascertain%20facts%20about%20the%20carnage%20in%20Manipur.%20Guess%20what%3F%20She%20has%20been%20threatened%20with%20arrest%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fsupreme-court-stays-arrest-of-woman-lawyer-who-went-to-manipur-as-part-of-fact-finding-team-and-held-press-meet%2Farticle67066876.ece%5C%22%3Ehad%20to%20petition%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20restraint%20order.%20The%20arrested%20accused%20%E2%80%93%20how%20soon%20they%20will%20get%20bail%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20conjecture%2C%20but%20they%20will%2C%20or%20at%20least%20a%20show%20of%20compassion.%20Remember%20the%20rapists%20and%20murderers%20in%20the%20Bilkis%20Bano%20case%3F%20After%20getting%20freedom%2C%20they%20will%20be%20garlanded%20and%20given%20%3Cem%3Eladdoos%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20teaching%20women%20a%20lesson%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebeti%20padhao%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fmadan-b-lokur%5C%22%3EJustice%20Madan%20B.%20Lokur%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20former%20judge%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Cou