0salary%20of%20Rs%2060%20per%20month%20and%20unparalleled%20satisfaction%2C%20Nayak%20dreamt%20of%20making%20a%20movie%20someday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20600px)%20100vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FManu-5-1689943704.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20movie%20poster%20of%20Kahi%20Debe%20Sandesh%20(1965)%20by%20Manu%20Nayak%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FManu-5-1689943704.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FManu-5-1689943704-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FManu-5-1689943704-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FManu-5-1689943704-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324751%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20movie%20poster%20of%20Kahi%20Debe%20Sandesh%20(1965)%20by%20Manu%20Nayak%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Wikipedia%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrawanshi%20wrote%20that%20Nayak%E2%80%99s%20motive%20behind%20making%20this%20film%20was%20as%20follows%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EKahi%20Debe%20Sandes%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1965)%20is%20a%20commentary%20on%20social%20issues%20such%20as%20Untouchability%20and%20Caste%20discrimination.%20I%20had%20seen%20it%20happening%20even%20in%20my%20own%20house.%20Whenever%20my%20friends%20from%20the%20lower%20castes%20(Satnami%20caste)%20used%20to%20come%20to%20my%20home%2C%20my%20mother%20used%20to%20not%20say%20anything%20but%20soon%20after%20they%20had%20left%20she%20used%20to%20clean%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20house.%20This%20and%20a%20few%20other%20instances%20deeply%20affected%20me%20and%20I%20realised%20that%20until%20caste%20discrimination%20is%20addressed%20properly%20to%20the%20masses%2C%20society%20would%20not%20progress.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20intent%20on%20these%20issues%20seeing%20the%20light%20of%20day%2C%20Nayak%20began%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F291630%2Fsanober-pardiwalla-bollywood-stuntwoman-for-actress-alia-bhatt-deepika-padukone-movies%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equest%20of%20casting%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20song%20recorded%20with%20legend%20Mohammed%20Rafi%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3EJhamkat%20nadiya%20bahini%20laage%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94%20a%20quick%20casting%20of%20theatre%20actors%20who%20were%20willing%2C%20and%20a%20record%2022-day%20packed%20shoot%20schedule%2C%20%3Cem%3EKahi%20Debe%20Sandesh%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20ready%20to%20roll.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Nayak%20says%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20spent%20the%20next%20two%20years%20paying%20off%20my%20debts.%20But%20I%20had%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20making%20the%20first%20Chhattisgarhi%20film.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261909%2Findia-film-project-ritam-bhatanagar-asia-largest-film-festival-content-creators%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20film%3C%2Fa%3E%20continues%20to%20stand%20by%20its%20legacy%20of%20being%20among%20the%20first%20to%20shed%20light%20on%20caste%20discrimination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20cinema%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20narratives%20highlighted%20in%20caste%20movies%2C%20as%20Sanjiv%20Jaiswal%2C%20director%20of%20%3Cem%3EShudra%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2012)%20emphasised%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EOutlook%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20dare%20to%20make%20films%20like%20these%20%5BShudra%5D%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20put%20the%20spotlight%20on%20the%20discriminated%20communities.%20There%20is%20a%20marked%20shift%20in%20how%20these%20movies%20are%20made%20today.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F256049%2Fdangal-to-baahubali-mumbai-artist-uses-mundane-items-to-create-magic-in-3000-movies%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20storylines%3C%2Fa%3E%20give%20the%20communities%20depicted%20greater%20agency%20and%20power%20over%20the%20story.%20This%20is%20a%20big%20change%20from%20the%20past%2C%20when%20either%20their%20entire%20existence%20would%20be%20ignored%2C%20or%20portrayed%20in%20poor%20light%2C%20causing%20more%20harm%20than%20good%20for%20these%20sections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhomegrown.co.in%2Fhomegrown-creators%2Fhow-the-first-chhattisgarhi-film-tackled-casteism-in-the-1960s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHow%20The%20First%20Chhattisgarhi%20Film%20Tackled%20Casteism%20In%20The%201960s%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Disha%20Bijolia%2C%20Published%20on%2020%20March%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Ffilm%2Fhow-first-chhattisgarhi-film-questioned-caste%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMedium%20and%20the%20Message%20by%20Caravan%20Magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Published%20on%202%20December%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fwhen-indira-saved-first-chhattisgarhi-film-from-ban%2Fa